bout%20the%20serious%20ethnic%20conflict%20in%20Manipur%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20the%20house%20and%20allow%20for%20an%20open%20discussion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Congress%20is%20a%20part%20of%20the%20recently%20announced%20INDIA%20alliance%20of%2026%20opposition%20parties%2C%20the%20BRS%20is%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20has%20a%20clear%20majority%20in%20parliament%2C%20so%20the%20opposition%20cannot%20be%20hoping%20to%20win%20the%20motion.%20So%20what%20is%20the%20agenda%20behind%20it%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20breaks%20down%20how%20the%20opposition%20may%20be%20trying%20to%20make%20some%20valuable%20points%20by%20filing%20a%20no-confidence%20motion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1.%20It%20helps%20establish%20the%20fact%20that%20governments%20come%20and%20go%20and%20are%20accountable.%20There%20is%20nothing%20%E2%80%98perpetual%E2%80%99%20or%20forever%20about%20any%20government%2C%20even%20if%20it%20has%20won%20a%20majority%2C%20twice%2C%20running.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2.%20The%20prime%20minister%20does%20not%20address%20Parliament%20and%20frequently%20picks%20%E2%80%98address%20to%20the%20nation%E2%80%99%20modes%2C%20like%20YouTube%20or%20his%20own%20social%20media%20channels%20%E2%80%93%20or%20outside%20Parliament%20%E2%80%93%20as%20stages%20for%20policy%20or%20other%20announcements.%20The%20%E2%80%98temple%20of%20democracy%E2%80%99%20is%20spoken%20of%20and%20worshipped%2C%20but%20its%20value%20as%20an%20institution%20that%20can%20be%20a%20check%20on%20the%20Executive%20is%20under%20serious%20questioning.%20Global%20Indices%20on%20Democracy%20whether%20V-Dem%2C%20Freedom%20House%20or%20International%20IDEA%20have%20recorded%20the%20decline%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20Parliament%20as%20a%20check%20on%20government.%20A%20motion%20like%20this%2C%20how%20it%20is%20handled%2C%20draws%20attention%20to%20the%20institution%20and%20its%20ways%20and%20forces%20the%20ruling%20party%20to%20be%20careful%20about%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3.%20There%20is%20a%20drive%20to%20establish%20which%20opposition%20party%20is%20really%20the%20one%20which%20is%20anti%20BJP.%20There%20is%20a%20vast%20line%20of%20%E2%80%98middlers%E2%80%99%2C%20parties%20like%20BRS%2C%20YSRCP%2C%20BJD%20and%20numerous%20others%2C%20not%20amongst%20the%20new%20NDA%20(38)%20or%20INDIA%20(26)%20parties%20that%20are%20then%20forced%20to%20take%20a%20call%20and%20show%20their%20cards.%20This%20helps%20draw%20the%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E4.%20Within%20INDIA%20too%2C%20there%20is%20Little%20INDIA%2C%20some%20doubts%20and%20concerns%20about%20certain%20parties%2C%20about%20where%20they%20really%20stand.%20For%20example%2C%20a%20sizeable%20faction%20of%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20is%20now%20with%20the%20BJP%20government%20in%20Maharashtra%20and%20there%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20interest%20in%20which%20way%20things%20will%20go.%20This%20helps%20establish%20who%20is%20standing%20where.%20As%20whatever%20may%20be%20the%20chances%20of%20winning%20it%2C%20no%20government%20can%20take%20a%20no-confidence%20motion%20non-seriously.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690353017000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F16103200%2FGlimpses_of_the_new_Parliament_Building_in_New_Delhi_2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhy-a-no-confidence-motion-now-four-tactical-advantages-the-opposition-might-be-aiming-for%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22There%20is%20no%20expectation%20amongst%20the%20opposition%20parties%20that%20it%20will%20be%20won.%20The%20difference%20is%20clear.%20BJP%20commands%20a%20majority%20of%20its%20own%2C%20well%20clear%20of%20the%20272%20mark%20(let%20alone%20majority%20amongst%20those%20present%20and%20voting).%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhy-a-no-confidence-motion-now-four-tactical-advantages-the-opposition-might-be-aiming-for%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%222019%20Video%20Of%20PM%20Modi's%20%5C%22Prediction%5C%22%20On%20No-Confidence%20Vote%20Goes%20Viral%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20day%20two%20notices%20for%20a%20no-confidence%20motion%20against%20the%20government%20were%20filed%20in%20parliament%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20comment%20in%20parliament%20in%202019%20has%20gone%20viral%2C%20with%20many%20in%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20calling%20it%20his%20%26quot%3Bprediction%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20video%20from%207%20February%202019%20of%20a%20debate%20on%20the%20President's%20speech%20during%20the%20Budget%20session%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20is%20heard%20saying%20that%20the%20opposition%20should%20prepare%20for%20yet%20another%20no%20trust%20motion%20in%202023.%20He%20was%20referring%20to%20his%20government%20defeating%20such%20a%20motion%20the%20year%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20offer%20my%20best%20wishes...%20prepare%20so%20much%20that%20you%20get%20a%20chance%20to%20bring%20a%20no-confidence%20again%20in%202023%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20drawing%20laughter%20and%20desk-thumping%20from%20ruling%20party%20MPs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20Samarpan%20Bhav%20(service)%20that%20from%20two%20(MPs)%20we%20are%20sitting%20here%20(in%20power).%20And%20the%20result%20of%20ahankar%20(arrogance)%20is%20that%20from%20400%2C%20you%20have%20come%20down%20to%2040.%20Look%20where%20you%20are%20today...%26quot%3B%20he%20sneered%2C%20without%20naming%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20was%20present%20along%20with%20other%20senior%20party%20leaders%20when%20the%20PM%20made%20the%20comments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20the%20government%20won%20a%20no%20confidence%20vote%20moved%20by%20the%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20(TDP)%20of%20N%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20and%20backed%20by%20many%20opposition%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20video%20of%20the%20statement%20was%20shared%20by%20government%20sources%20who%20called%20it%20PM%20Modi's%20%26quot%3Bprediction%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20time%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20filed%20a%20no-trust%20motion%20against%20the%20Modi%20government%20amid%20a%20deadlock%20over%20Manipur.%20Though%20the%20motion%20backed%20by%20the%20INDIA%20coalition%20of%20opposition%20parties%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20defeated%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20where%20the%20government%20enjoys%20a%20big%20majority%2C%20leaders%20said%20the%20move%20was%20aimed%20at%20forcing%20PM%20Modi%20to%20make%20a%20statement%20on%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ongoing%20ethnic%20clashes%20in%20Manipur%20have%20been%20a%20key%20reason%20for%20the%20continuous%20logjam%20in%20both%20of%20Parliament%20since%20the%20Monsoon%20Session%20began%20on%20July%2020.%20A%20day%20before%20the%20session%2C%20a%20horrific%20video%20of%20two%20women%20paraded%20naked%20by%20a%20mob%20in%20Manipur%20went%20viral%2C%20provoking%20nationwide%20outrage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20separate%20no-confidence%20motion%20has%20been%20filed%20by%20Telangana%20Chief%20Minister%20K%20Chandrasekhar%20Rao's%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20(BRS)%2C%20which%20is%20not%20a%20part%20of%20the%20'I.N.D.I.A'%20coalition.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690352700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F8lv5cuv_pm-modi-2019-prediction_625x300_26_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F2019-video-of-pm-modis-prediction-on-no-confidence-vote-goes-viral-4240728%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22On%20a%20day%20two%20notices%20for%20a%20no-confidence%20motion%20against%20the%20government%20were%20filed%20in%20parliament%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20comment%20in%20parliament%20in%202019%20has%20gone%20viral%2C%20with%20many%20in%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20calling%20it%20his%20%26quot%3Bprediction%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%