%20was%20way%20too%20much%2C%20it%20was%20a%20big%20event%20under%20ICC.%20With%20the%20punishment%2C%20you%20set%20an%20example%20for%20the%20future.%20You%20can%20get%20aggressive%20on%20cricket%3B%20controlled%20aggression%20is%20good%2C%20but%20this%20was%20a%20bit%20too%20much%2C%26quot%3B%20Afridi%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D2AJERHQi3bs%5C%22%3ESamaa%20TV%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%20of%20the%20accumulation%20of%204%20demerit%20points%2C%20Harmanpreet%20was%20automatically%20suspended%20for%20the%20next%20two%20limited-overs%20games.%20As%20per%20the%20ruling%2C%20a%20player%20who%20gets%204%20demerit%20points%2C%20is%20to%20miss%20one%20Test%20or%20two%20ODIs%20or%202%20T20Is%2C%20whichever%20come%20next.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20suspension%2C%20however%2C%20comes%20at%20the%20wrong%20time%20for%20the%20Indian%20women's%20team%20which%20is%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20Asian%20Games%20next.%20Having%20already%20qualified%20for%20the%20quarter-finals%2C%20the%20team%20will%20no%20be%20without%20the%20services%20of%20its%20captain%20for%20the%20two%20knockout%20games.%20In%20a%20case%20India%20do%20manage%20to%20qualify%20for%20the%20final%2C%20Harmanpreet%20would%20be%20able%20to%20play.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690352100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-12%2Fmaooi3r8_shahid-afridi-_625x300_25_December_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fthis-is-not-just-india-shahid-afridi-on-harmanpreet-kaur-controversy-4240383%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indian%20women's%20cricket%20team%20captain%20Harmanpreet%20Kaur%20continues%20to%20be%20criticised%20over%20her%20behaviour%20in%20the%203rd%20ODI%20against%20Bangladesh.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fthis-is-not-just-india-shahid-afridi-on-harmanpreet-kaur-controversy-4240383%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fthis-is-not-just-india-shahid-afridi-on-harmanpreet-kaur-controversy-4240383%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fthis-is-not-just-india-shahid-afridi-on-harmanpreet-kaur-controversy-4240383%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20The%20Electoral%20Math%20Of%20INDIA%20vs%20NDA%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20contest%20for%202024%20is%20heating%20up%20as%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP%20both%20finalising%20their%20alliances.%20A%2026-party%20consortium%20named%20%26quot%3BINDIA%26quot%3B%20is%20set%20to%20compete%20with%20a%2038-party%20NDA%2C%20offering%20voters%20an%20option%20they%20didn't%20have%20in%202019.%20The%20presence%20of%20the%20Congress%20in%20%26quot%3BINDIA%26quot%3B%20lends%20stability%20to%20the%20opposition%20alliance%2C%20and%20the%20reassures%20voters%20that%2C%20given%20a%20chance%2C%20they%20can%20complete%20a%20full%20five-year%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Does%20The%20Math%20Look%20Like%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UPA%2C%20in%20its%20earlier%20avatar%20in%202019%2C%20bagged%2091%20seats%20with%20a%2027%25%20vote%20share.%20The%20rebranded%20INDIA%20has%20144%20MPs%20in%20the%20545-member%20Lok%20Sabha%20with%20a%2037.5%25%20vote%20share.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20NDA%20won%20353%20seats%20with%20a%2045%25%20vote%20share.%20Changes%20like%20the%20exit%20of%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20and%20Uddhav%20Thackeray's%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20and%20the%20entry%20of%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20NCP%20faction%2C%20bring%20down%20that%20tally%20to%20332%20seats%20with%20a%2042.9%25%20vote%20share.%20The%20mammoth%2018%25%20lead%20enjoyed%20by%20the%20NDA%20shrinks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22lneeo3s8%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Flneeo3s8_graph-1_625x300_26_July_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECategory%20of%20Contests%20in%202024%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20four%20categories%20of%20contests%20likely%20in%202024%2C%20based%20on%20the%202019%20numbers.%20In%20375%20seats%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20in%20contention%2C%20while%20the%20Congress%20will%20be%20in%20the%20game%20in%20261%20seats.%20Regional%20parties%2C%20whether%20in%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20or%20the%20NDA%2C%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20in%20contention%20in%20353%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22p3n71i3%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fp3n71i3_graph-2_625x300_26_July_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECategory%201%20(BJP%20vs%20Congress)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20and%20Congress%20locked%20horns%20in%20190%20seats%20in%202019.%20The%20BJP%20won%20175%20while%20the%20Congress%2C%2017.%20The%20BJP%20recorded%20a%20lead%20of%20more%20than%2020%25%20in%20terms%20of%20vote%20share%20in%20these%20seats.%20The%20party%20that%20ranked%203rd%20won%2C%20on%20average%2C%20just%20a%204%25%20vote%20share%2C%20implying%20these%20were%20mainly%20BJP%20versus%20Congress%20contests%20with%20limited%20role%20of%20regional%20parties%20in%20states%20like%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20Uttarakhand%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Delhi%2C%20Goa%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20Assam%2C%20Haryana%2C%20and%20parts%20of%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20party's%20alliances%20are%20unlikely%20to%20bear%20fruits%20there%20and%20it%20is%20largely%20on%20its%20own.%20Its%20allies%20in%20INDIA%2C%20like%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%2C%20Trinamool%20Congress%2C%20and%20the%20Left%20parties%20have%20limited%20presence%20there.%20However%2C%20the%20third%20ranked%20party%20secured%20more%20votes%20than%20the%20margin%20of%20victory%20in%2019%20seats%2C%20and%2013%20were%20won%20by%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22qipolq7%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fqipolq7_graph-3-_625x300_26_July_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECategory%202%20(BJP%20vs%20Regional%20Parties)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20and%20regional%20parties%20contested%20on%20185%20seats%20in%202019%2C%20the%20BJP%20won%20128%20while%20regional%20parties%2057.%20The%20BJP%20had%20a%20lead%20of%207%25%20in%20vote%20share%20terms%20on%20these%20seats.%20The%20party%20that%20ranked%203rd%20won%20a%20similar%20vote%20share%2C%20indicating%20that%20alliances%20could%20be%20a%20game%20changer%20there%2C%20mainly%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Odisha%2C%20parts%20of%20Bihar%20and%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22pqv0371o%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fpqv0371o_graph-4_625x300_26_July_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20party%20was%20ranked%203rd%20on%2088%20seats%20here.%20The%20number%20three%20party%20secured%20more%20votes%20than%20the%20margin%20of%20victory%20in%2055%20seats%2C%20and%2030%20of%20them%20were%20won%20by%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECategory%203%20(Congress%20vs%20Regional%20Parties)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20and%20regional%20parties%20contested%2071%20seats%20in%202019.%20The%20Congress%20won%2037%20while%20regional%20parties%2034.%20In%20terms%20of%20vote%20share%2C%20it%20was%20neck-and-neck%20with%20both%20securing%2041%25%20each.%20The%20party%20ranked%20third%20recorded%20an%20almost%2012%25%20vote%20share%2C%20spoiling%20the%20chances%20of%20the%20runner-up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20these%20states%20like%20Telangana%2C%20Punjab%2C%20parts%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Kerala%2C%20Bihar%20etc.%20there%20is%20limited%20benefit%20of%20alliances%2C%20or%20they%20are%20already%20in%20place%2C%20or%20they%20are%20difficult%20to%20forge.%20The%20third%20ranked%20party%20secured%20more%20votes%20than%20the%20margin%20of%20victory%20in%2032%20seats%2C%20and%2021%20of%20them%20were%20won%20by%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECategory%204%20(Regional%20vs%20Regional)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegional%20parties%20contested%20against%20each%20other%20in%2097%20seats%20in%202019.%20In%2059%20of%20them%2C%20it%20was%20a%20UPA%20versus%20NDA%20contest.%20The%20difference%20in%20vote%20shares%20between%20the%20winner%20and%20runner-up%20was%2015%25%2C%20with%20the%20third%20party%20securing%20just%207%25%20vote%20share.%20The%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP%20were%20third%20on%20only%20nine%20and%20five%20seats%20respectively%20and%20had%20a%20meagre%200.3%25%20vote%20share%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlliances%20are%20already%20set%20here%20like%20Bihar%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20but%20changes%20in%20dynamics%20play%20a%20role%20here%20as%20some%20allies%20have%20crisscrossed%20like%20JD(U)%2C%20Sena%20and%20NCP.%20The%20third-ranked%20party%20secured%20more%20votes%20than%20the%20margin%20of%20victory%20in%2024%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPM%20Modi's%20Call%20For%2050%25%2B%20vote%20share%20for%20NDA%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncluding%20the%20Category%201%20and%202%20seats%20where%20the%20BJP%20won%20303%2C%20it%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20a%20close%20fight%20in%2043%20of%20these%20seats%2C%20where%20the%20BJP%20placed%20third%20and%20spoiled%20the%20chances%20of%20the%20Congress%20(13)%20and%20regional%20parties%20(30).%20These%20seats%20could%20swing%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20set%20a%20target%20of%2050%25%20plus%20for%20the%20NDA%20in%20the%202024%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20could%20brush%20it%20off%2C%20the%20BJP's%20vote%20share%20is%20set%20to%20increase%20as%20the%20party%20will%20be%20contesting%20more%20seats%20in%20Bihar%2C%20Maharashtra%20and%20Punjab%2C%20where%20allies%20have%20walked%20out.%20The%20target%20shouldn't%20be%20taken%20lightly%20by%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20parties%20as%20the%20BJP%20achieved%20a%20similar%20feat%20in%20Gujarat%202022%2C%20when%20political%20pundits%20thought%20it%20had%20peaked.%20In%20Bihar%20alone%20it%20can%20gain%20a%201-1.5%25%20vote%20share.%20As%20the%20BJP%20knows%20its%20opponents%2010%20months%20in%20advance%2C%20it%20has%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20to%20prepare%20and%20strategise%20to%20neutralise%20impact%20of%20opposition%20parties%20coming%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EScenario%20Analysis%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20starts%20with%20a%20base%20of%20303%20seats.%20If%20there%20is%20a%205%20per%20cent%20swing%20against%20the%20BJP%20on%20the%20seats%20it%20won%20in%202019%2C%20(implying%20the%20BJP's%20vote%20share%20declines%20by%205%25%20and%20runner-up's%20vote%20share%20increases%20by%205%25)%2C%20the%20BJP's%20tally%20could%20decline%20by%2080%20seats%2C%20to%20223.%20The%20swing%20could%20be%20due%20to%20local%20level%20anti-incumbency%2C%20the%20increase%20in%20popularity%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%20an%20inactive%20BJP%20cadre%20over-dependent%20on%20Modi%2C%20the%20Congress%20party's%20five%20promises%20gaining%20traction%20etc.%20To%20note%2C%20as%20per%20polls%20conducted%20post%20Karnataka%20results%2C%20including%20by%20CSDS%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi's%20popularity%20and%20NDA's%20vote%20share%20remains%20intact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22jf4a3f48%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fjf4a3f48_graph-5_625x300_26_July_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20if%20there%20is%20a%205%25%20swing%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20BJP%20on%20the%20seats%20where%20it%20finished%20as%20a%20runner%20up%20in%202019%2C%20(implying%20the%20BJP's%20vote%20share%20increases%20by%205%25%20and%20the%20winner's%20vote%20share%20declines%20by%205%25)%2C%20the%20BJP's%20tally%20could%20improve%20by%2039%20seats%20to%20342.%20The%20swing%20could%20be%20due%20to%20a%20range%20of%20factors%20including%20pro-incumbency%2C%20the%20increase%20in%20popularity%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20and%20the%20NDA%2C%20new%20schemes%20to%20tackle%20issues%20like%20inflation%2C%20unemployment%2C%20corruption%2C%20and%20differences%20within%20the%20INDIA%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20effect%2C%20the%20BJP's%20range%20seems%20to%20be%20223%20seats%20(lower%20end)%20to%20342%20seats%20(upper%20end)%20depending%20upon%20how%20things%20shape%20up%20in%20the%20next%2010%20months%20and%20who%20seizes%20the%20narrative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Amitabh%20Tiwari%20is%20a%20political%20strategist%20and%20commentator.%20In%20his%20earlier%20avatar%20he%20was%20a%20corporate%20and%20investment%20banker.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690352040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F1subjt2_opposition-meet_625x300_19_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fopinion-the-electoral-math-of-india-vs-nda-4240701%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20contest%20for%202024%20is%20heating%20up%20as%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP%20both%20finalising%20their%20alliances.%20A%2026-party%20consortium%20named%20%26quot%3BINDIA%26quot%3B%20is%20set%20to%20compete%20with%20a%2038-party%20NDA%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fopinion-the-electoral-math-of-india-vs-nda-4240701%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fopinion-the-electoral-math-of-india-vs-nda-4240701%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fopinion-the-electoral-math-of-india-vs-nda-4240701%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Union%20Govt%20Moves%20SC%20to%20Extend%20ED%20Director%20S.K.%20Mishra's%20Tenure%20Days%20After%20'Illegal'%20Ruling%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2F15174623%2FSKMishra_EDdirector_141120_1200.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Union%20government%20has%20moved%20Supreme%20Court%20seeking%20the%20extension%20of%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%E2%80%99s%20chief%2C%20S.K.%20Mishra%E2%80%99s%20tenure%20in%20office%2C%20days%20after%20the%20apex%20court%20ruled%20that%20earlier%20extensions%20given%20to%20him%20had%20been%20illegal%20and%20that%20he%20cannot%20be%20allowed%20to%20stay%20on%20in%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20through%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLiveLawIndia%2Fstatus%2F1684070130219884545%5C%22%3Etweet%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Solicitor%20General%20Tushar%20Mehta%20told%20the%20court%20today%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20is%20filing%20an%20application%20with%20regards%20to%20the%20recent%20judgment%20on%20Mishra%E2%80%99s%20tenure.%20Requesting%20this%20application%20to%20be%20listed%20in%20front%20of%20the%20court%20before%20Friday%2C%20July%2028%2C%20SG%20Mehta%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20making%20some%20prayer%20that%20will%20have%20to%20persuade%20this%20court.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20agreed%20to%20list%20it%20at%203.30%20pm%20tomorrow%2C%20July%2027.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMishra%E2%80%99s%20term%20will%20end%20on%20July%2031.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20July%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-enforcement-directorate-sk-mishra-extensions-illegal%5C%22%3Eheld%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20extensions%20given%20to%20Mishra%20after%20its%20own%20earlier%20order%20barring%20further%20extensions%20were%20invalid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20three-judge%20bench%20of%20Justices%20B.R.%20Gavai%2C