l%20network%20to%20Oppenheimer.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Felon-musk-mocks-barbie-over-its-anti-patriarchy-message-4240689%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Felon-musk-mocks-barbie-over-its-anti-patriarchy-message-4240689%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Felon-musk-mocks-barbie-over-its-anti-patriarchy-message-4240689%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Explained%3A%20How%20Does%20A%20No-Confidence%20Motion%20Work%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20party%2C%20as%20part%20of%20the%20newly%20formed%20INDIA%20opposition%20alliance%2C%20along%20with%20Telangana's%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20(BRS)%2C%20have%20filed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-kcrs-party-file-no-trust-motion-against-government-in-lok-sabha-amid-parliament-impasse-over-manipur-4240464%5C%22%3Etwo%20separate%20no-confidence%20motions%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20the%20Narendra%20Modi-led%20government%20in%20Lok%20Sabha.%20This%20move%20comes%20amidst%20the%20ongoing%20parliamentary%20impasse%20over%20the%20ethnic%20clashes%20in%20Manipur%20that%20have%20left%20over%20125%20people%20dead%2C%20thousands%20displaced%20and%20new%20tales%20of%20unspeakable%20horrors%20each%20day.%20The%20conflict%2C%20and%20the%20government's%20inability%20to%20end%20it%20even%20after%20three%20months%20of%20violence%2C%20has%20been%20a%20key%20reason%20for%20the%20continuous%20logjam%20in%20both%20houses%20of%20parliament%20since%20the%20monsoon%20session%20began%20on%20July%2020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20no-confidence%20motion%20by%20opposition%20parties%20being%20likely%20to%20fail%20the%20numbers%20test%2C%20they%20argue%20that%20they%20will%20win%20the%20%26quot%3Bbattle%20of%20perception%26quot%3B%20by%20cornering%20the%20government%20on%20the%20Manipur%20issue%20during%20the%20debate.%20The%20opposition%20contends%20that%20this%20strategy%20will%20compel%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20to%20address%20the%20crucial%20matter%20in%20parliament%2C%20despite%20the%20government's%20insistence%20that%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20will%20respond%20to%20the%20debate%20on%20the%20Manipur%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EThe%20Current%20Numbers%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20majority%20mark%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20at%20272%2C%20the%20PM%20Modi's%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20government%20is%20safe%20with%20331%20members.%20The%20BJP%20alone%20has%20303.%20The%20opposition%20INDIA%20alliance%20has%20144%20while%20parties%20like%20KCR's%20BRS%2C%20YS%20Jagan%20Reddy's%20YSRCP%20and%20Naveen%20Patnaik's%20BJD%20have%20combined%20strength%20of%2070.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EUnderstanding%20the%20No-Confidence%20Motion%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20no-confidence%20motion%20is%20a%20parliamentary%20tool%20used%20by%20the%20opposition%20to%20express%20its%20lack%20of%20confidence%20in%20the%20government.%20The%20ruling%20party%20must%20then%20prove%20its%20majority%20in%20the%20House%20to%20maintain%20confidence.%20If%20it%20loses%20the%20majority%2C%20the%20government%20will%20fall%20immediately.%20The%20government%20can%20remain%20in%20power%20as%20long%20as%20it%20has%20the%20majority%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EThe%20Opposition's%20Weapon%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOften%20used%20as%20a%20strategic%20tool%20by%20the%20opposition%2C%20the%20no-confidence%20motion%20allows%20them%20to%20question%20the%20ruling%20government%2C%20highlight%20their%20failures%2C%20and%20discuss%20them%20in%20the%20house.%20This%20motion%20also%20plays%20a%20significant%20role%20in%20uniting%20the%20opposition.%20If%20the%20motion%20is%20passed%20in%20the%20House%2C%20the%20entire%20cabinet%2C%20including%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20must%20resign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3ELok%20Sabha's%20Exclusive%20Right%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20Article%2075%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20the%20Cabinet%20is%20collectively%20accountable%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%20Only%20the%20opposition%20can%20bring%20this%20proposal%2C%20and%20it%20can%20be%20introduced%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20only%2C%20not%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20Any%20party%20in%20parliament%20can%20move%20a%20no-confidence%20motion%20against%20the%20government%2C%20and%20the%20ruling%20government%20must%20prove%20its%20majority%20to%20stay%20in%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EThe%20Procedure%20For%20A%20No-Confidence%20Motion%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20no-confidence%20motion%20is%20brought%20according%20to%20the%20rules%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%20Under%20rules%20198(1)%20and%20198(5)%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20it%20can%20be%20introduced%20only%20after%20the%20Speaker%20has%20called%20upon%20it.%20The%20information%20about%20bringing%20it%20to%20the%20House%20has%20to%20be%20given%20in%20writing%20to%20the%20Secretary-General%20by%2010%20am.%20It%20requires%20the%20support%20of%20at%20least%2050%20members%20of%20the%20House.%20If%20the%20motion%20is%20passed%2C%20the%20President%20fixes%20one%20or%20more%20days%20for%20discussion.%20The%20President%20of%20India%20can%20also%20ask%20the%20government%20to%20prove%20its%20majority.%20If%20the%20government%20is%20unable%20to%20do%20so%2C%20the%20cabinet%20must%20resign%2C%20or%20else%20it%20will%20be%20dismissed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EImpact%20Of%20No-Confidence%20Motions%20On%20Previous%20Governments%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20no-confidence%20motion%20has%20historically%20been%20used%20as%20a%20form%20of%20protest%20to%20keep%20the%20government%20accountable.%20It%20has%20been%20instrumental%20in%20toppling%20governments%2C%20especially%20when%20coalition%20governments%20started%20to%20form.%20From%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%2C%20the%20country's%20first%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20to%20Narendra%20Modi%20in%202018%2C%20several%20leaders%20have%20faced%20this%20proposal.%20While%20some%20survived%2C%20others%20like%20Morarji%20Desai%2C%20Charan%20Singh%2C%20VP%20Singh%2C%20and%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20saw%20their%20governments%20fall%20due%20to%20no-confidence%20motions.%20The%20last%20no-confidence%20motion%20faced%20by%20the%20Narendra%20Modi-led%20NDA%20government%20in%202018%20was%20defeated%20by%20199%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690351860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-01%2Fcjob5qi_parliament-reuters-generic_625x300_17_January_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-how-does-a-no-confidence-motion-work-4240688%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Often%20used%20as%20a%20strategic%20tool%20by%20the%20opposition%2C%20the%20no-confidence%20motion%20allows%20them%20to%20question%20the%20ruling%20government%2C%20highlight%20their%20failures%2C%20and%20discuss%20them%20in%20the%20house.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-how-does-a-no-confidence-motion-work-4240688%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-how-does-a-no-confidence-motion-work-4240688%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-how-does-a-no-confidence-motion-work-4240688%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India-Pak%20ODI%20WC%20clash%20may%20be%20advanced%20due%20to%20Navratri%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690351849000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102128269%2Cimgsize-41744.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Ficc-world-cup%2Findia-pakistan-odi-world-cup-clash-may-be-advanced-due-to-navratri-celebrations-in-ahmedabad%2Farticleshow%2F102128085.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20highly%20anticipated%20India-Pakistan%20contest%20in%20the%20upcoming%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20might%20be%20advanced%20by%20a%20day%20to%20October%2014%20due%20to%20the%20opening%20day%20of%20Navratri%20celebrations%20in%20Ahmedabad.%20The%20ICC%20and%20the%20BCCI%20had%20earlier%20announced%20the%20World%20Cup%20schedule%2C%20with%20the%20marquee%20clash%20to%20take%20place%20at%20the%20world's%20largest%20stadium%20in%20Ahmedabad.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Ficc-world-cup%2Findia-pakistan-odi-world-cup-clash-may-be-advanced-due-to-navratri-celebrations-in-ahmedabad%2Farticleshow%2F102128085.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Impose%20Conditions%20on%20Recipients%20of%20Govt%20Honours%20to%20Prevent%20'Award%20Wapsi'%3A%20Parliamentary%20Panel%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2Fdelhi.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EA%20parliamentary%20committee%20has%20recommended%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20put%20a%20system%20in%20place%20to%20take%20prior%20undertakings%20from%20shortlisted%20candidates%20for%20government%20awards%20to%20avoid%20an%20%E2%80%98award-wapsi-like%20situation%E2%80%99%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20system%20may%20be%20put%20in%20place%20where%20an%20undertaking%20is%20taken%20from%20the%20proposed%20awardee%20citing%20acceptance%20of%20the%20award%20and%20that%20the%20awardees%20cannot%20dishonor%20the%20award%20at%20any%20point%20of%20time%20in%20future%2C%E2%80%9D%C2%A0stated%20a%20report%20tabled%20in%20parliament%20by%20the%20parliamentary%20committee%20on%20transport%2C%20tourism%2C%20and%20culture%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fparliamentary-committee-recommends-prior-undertakings-from-recipients-cultural-institutions-academies-2411480-2023-07-25%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EIndia%20Today%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20report%20by%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tribuneindia.com%2Fnews%2Fnation%2Fwary-of-award-wapsi-parliamentary-committee-wants-undertaking-from-recipients-529065%3F_gl%3D1*d6iqub*_ga*OUJWNVBJbWNyV25nSlBsSy1ONHk2QkVDS3lXaXVOWi1mMzFhdFdUdE5mVHdqZ3FQd0xqREZpMjJnU0VidnA0dg%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%20Tribune%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20further%20quoted%20the%20committee%20as%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CAwards%20may%20not%20be%20given%20without%20such%20an%20undertaking.%20In%20the%20event%20that%20the%20awards%20are%20returned%2C%20the%20awardee%20shall%20not%20be%20considered%20for%20such%20an%20award%20in%20the%20future.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20termed%20the%20act%20of%20returning%20awards%20in%20protest%20against%20political%20issues%20%E2%80%9Cdisgraceful%20to%20the%20country%E2%80%9D.%20While%20noting%20that%20political%20issues%20are%20outside%20the%20ambit%20of%20the%20cultural%20realms%2C%20returning%20awards%2C%20according%20to%20the%20committee%2C%20would%20impact%20the%20overall%20prestige%20and%20reputation%20of%20the%20awards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20parliamentary%20panel%20argued%20that%20it%20is%20important%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Creturn%20of%20the%20award%20is%20not%20used%20as%20an%20instrument%20of%20political%20protest%E2%80%9D%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Federal%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthefederal.com%2Fstates%2Fsouth%2Fkarnataka%2Faward-wapsi-clause-proposal-shocks-literary-cultural-fraternity-in-karnataka%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20report%20is%20titled%20%3Cem%3EFunctioning%20of%20National%20Akademies%20and%20Other%20Cultural%20Institutions%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarting%20from%20September%202015%2C%20eminent%20writers%2C%20filmmakers%2C%20and%20other%20prominent%20personalities%20returned%20awards%20given%20to%20them%20by%20the%20government%20to%20protest%20against%20the%20targeting%20of%20minorities%20and%20the%20spate%20of%20communal%20violence%20under%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government.%20Many%20prominent%20personalities%20also%20returned%20the%20honours%20bestowed%20on%20them%20by%20the%20government%20in%20protest%20specifically%20against%20the%20murders%20of%20rationalists%20like%20M.M.%20Kalburgi%2C%20Govind%20Pansare%20and%20Narendra%20Dabholkar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20them%20returned%20the%20plaque%20and%20others%20sent%20back%20the%20cheques%20of%20amounts%20they%20received%20as%20part%20of%20the%20award.%20The%20committee%20said%20it%20was%20informed%20by%20the%20Sahitya%20Akademi%20that%20it%20does%20not%20have%20any%20system%20for%20taking%20back%20the%20award.%20Therefore%2C%20cheques%20were%20not%20deposited%2C%20and%20there%20was%20no%20instance%20of%20%E2%80%9Caward%20wapsi%E2%80%9D%20after%202015%2C%20the%20committee%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20specifically%20noted%20that%2039%20recipients%20of%20the%20Sahitya%20Akademi%20Awards%20returned%20their%20awards%20in%202015%20to%20protest%20the%20murder%20of%20Kalburgi.%C2%A0%20The%20Committee%20said%20some%20of%20the%20awardees%20who%20had%20returned%20their%20awards%20continued%20their%20association%20with%20the%20Akademi%2C%20serving%20either%20on%20the%20jury%20or%20participating%20in%20the%20Akademi%E2%80%99s%20programmes.%20It%20questioned%20the%20re-engagement%20of%20such%20awardees%20who%20joined%20the%20Akademi%20%E2%80%9Cafter%20insulting%20it%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Federal%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20quoted%20several%20writers%2C%20filmmakers%2C%20academicians%2C%20theatre%2C%20and%20folk%20personalities%20of%20Karnataka%20who%20termed%20the%20recommendations%20of%20the%20panel%20as%20%E2%80%9Canti-democratic%2C%20an%20assault%20on%20freedom%20of%20expression%20and%20an%20attempt%20to%20curtail%20the%20freedom%20to%20protest%20in%20any%20form%20granted%20by%20the%20constitution%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAwards%20are%20primarily%20being%20conferred%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20achievement%20of%20personality%20in%20the%20specified%20field%20of%20art.%20The%20selection%20of%20the%20person%20is%20based%20on%20recommendation%20of%20a%20jury%20or%20selection%20committee.%20It%20is%20the%20responsibility%20of%20both%20the%20government%20and%20cultural%20institution%20not%20to%20humiliate%20personalities%20they%20chose%20for%20the%20award%20by%20imposing%20conditions.%20Karnataka%20has%20a%20history%20of%20respecting%20the%20creative%20freedom%20of%20cultural%20personalities%20and%20protecting%20them%20from%20any%20autocratic%20and%20undemocratic%20political%20dispensation%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20noted%20writer%20and%20cultural%20critic%20Baraguru%20Ramachandrappa.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690351820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2Fdelhi.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fimpose-conditions-on-recipients-of-govt-honours-to-prevent-award-wapsi-parliamentary-panel%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20parliamentary%20committee%20on%20transport%2C%20tourism%2C%20and%20culture%20said%20the%20government%20must%20ensure%20that%20the%20'return%20of%20the%20award%20is%20not%20used%20as%20an%20instrument%20of%20political%20protest'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fimpose-conditions-on-recipients-of-govt-honours-to-prevent-award-wapsi-parliamentary-panel%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Prakash%20Jha's%20father%20Tejnath%20passes%20away%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690351533000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102128070%2Cimgsize-98141.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Ftejnath-jha-father-of-producer-director-prakash-jha-passes-away-in-patna%2Farticleshow%2F102128113.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22htt