ad-and-several-injured-after-major-fire-on-cargo-ship-near-ameland-in-netherlands-12927537%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Byju's%20Founder%20Broke%20Down%20In%20Tears%20As%20Crises%20Engulfed%20Ed-Tech%20Startup%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20late%20April%2C%20Indian%20officials%20in%20plainclothes%20raided%20the%20Bengaluru%20offices%20of%20Byju's%2C%20seizing%20laptops%20and%20publicly%20linking%20the%20world's%20most%20valuable%20education-technology%20startup%20with%20possible%20foreign%20exchange%20violations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20ocean%20away%2C%20Byju%20Raveendran%2C%20the%20firm's%20eponymous%20founder%20and%20chief%20executive%2C%20paced%20his%20condo%20in%20Dubai%2C%20downing%20cups%20of%20black%20coffee%20and%20fielding%20calls%20from%20top%20investors.%20With%20a%20planned%20%241%20billion%20equity%20fundraise%20from%20Middle%20Eastern%20investors%20still%20in%20limbo%2C%20Raveendran%20broke%20down%20in%20tears%20defending%20his%20company%2C%20according%20to%20people%20who%20attended%20the%20calls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaveendran%20had%20been%20in%20crisis%20mode%20for%20months.%20Apart%20from%20the%20raid%20by%20India's%20financial%20crime-fighting%20agency%2C%20his%20once%20high-flying%20tutoring%20startup%20failed%20to%20file%20its%20financial%20accounts%20on%20time.%20Several%20US-based%20investors%20accused%20Byju's%20of%20hiding%20half%20a%20billion%20dollars%2C%20prompting%20lawsuits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20Prosus%20NV%2C%20one%20of%20the%20company's%20earliest%20investors%2C%20said%20it%20had%20given%20up%20its%20board%20seat%20because%20of%20poor%20governance%20and%20disregard%20for%20directors'%20advice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EByju's%20and%20Raveendran%20have%20denied%20wrongdoing.%20But%20their%20tale%20-%20pieced%20together%20from%20interviews%20with%20more%20than%20a%20dozen%20people%20involved%20in%20the%20firm's%20operations%20-%20is%20a%20window%20into%20challenges%20facing%20India's%20startups.%20With%20limited%20domestic%20venture%20capital%2C%20firms%20like%20Byju's%20have%20looked%20outward%20for%20support.%20That%20changed%20last%20year%2C%20when%20startup%20funding%20took%20a%20hit%2C%20falling%20to%20a%20four-year%20low%20by%20the%20first%20half%20of%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithout%20easy%20access%20to%20global%20capital%2C%20companies%20are%20now%20facing%20greater%20scrutiny%20over%20corporate%20governance%2C%20jeopardizing%20India's%20quest%20to%20pull%20even%20with%20the%20US%20and%20China%20as%20a%20tech%20capital%20of%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20situation%20is%20not%20contained%20quickly%20and%20guardrails%20are%20not%20put%20in%20place%20at%20Byju's%2C%20it%20will%20affect%20India's%20image%20as%20an%20investment%20destination%20among%20overseas%20funds%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jacob%20Mathew%2C%20a%20chairman%20of%20investment%20banking%20at%20Incred%20Capital%20Ltd.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaveendran's%20rise%20from%20a%20private%20tutor%20to%20the%20leader%20of%20a%20%2422%20billion%20company%20captivated%20global%20investors%2C%20including%20Sequoia%20Capital%2C%20Blackstone%20Inc.%20and%20Mark%20Zuckerberg's%20foundation.%20During%20the%20pandemic%2C%20Raveendran%20cornered%20a%20majority%20of%20the%20ed-tech%20market%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20after%20classrooms%20reopened%2C%20concerns%20about%20Byju's%20finances%20pricked%20at%20the%20firm's%20reputation.%20Investors%20questioned%20why%20Raveendran%20delayed%20hiring%20a%20chief%20financial%20officer%20for%20years%20and%20acquired%20more%20than%20a%20dozen%20companies%20across%20the%20world%20at%20break-neck%20speed.%20Scores%20of%20employees%20have%20either%20left%20or%20been%20fired.%20Board%20members%20have%20resigned.%20And%20many%20teaching%20centers%20are%20nearly%20empty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaveendran's%20supporters%20attribute%20missteps%20to%20the%20enthusiasm%20and%20naivete%20of%20an%20inexperienced%20founder%20who%20grew%20too%20quickly.%20Critics%20say%20he%20acted%20recklessly%20by%20withholding%20information%20about%20finances%20and%20failing%20to%20rigorously%20audit%20accounts.%20In%20India's%20startup%20world%2C%20many%20see%20Byju's%20as%20the%20highest-profile%20example%20of%20what%20happens%20when%20a%20business%20scales%20one%20of%20the%20fastest-growing%20economies%20during%20a%20boom%20%E2%80%94%20but%20fails%20to%20plan%20for%20a%20bust.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaveendran%20and%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20Byju's%20declined%20to%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUnusual%20Beginnings%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaveendran%20grew%20up%20in%20a%20village%20in%20the%20coastal%20state%20of%20Kerala%20and%20attended%20a%20local%20school%20where%20his%20father%20taught%20physics%20and%20his%20mother%20math.%20He%20was%20an%20unconventional%20student%2C%20according%20to%20people%20who%20knew%20him%20at%20the%20time%2C%20skipping%20classes%20to%20play%20football%20and%20preferring%20to%20teach%20himself%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20briefly%20working%20as%20an%20engineer%2C%20Raveendran%20began%20coaching%20students%20at%20a%20college%20in%20Bengaluru.%20Enrollment%20doubled%20every%20week%2C%20and%20Raveendran%20eventually%20moved%20classes%20into%20a%20sports%20stadium.%20Lessons%20were%20projected%20onto%20giant%20screens%20for%20thousands%20of%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaveendran's%20teaching%20methods%20stood%20out%20in%20India%2C%20where%20good%20instructors%20are%20scarce%20and%20methodologies%20antiquated.%20He%20was%20adept%20at%20preparing%20students%20for%20fiercely%20competitive%20entrance%20exams%20to%20premier%20engineering%20and%20medical%20colleges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaveendran%20recruited%20his%20best%20students%20to%20teach%20alongside%20him%20and%20opened%2041%20coaching%20centers.%20In%202011%2C%20he%20registered%20Think%20and%20Learn%20Pvt%20Ltd.%20-%C2%A0%20the%20parent%20company%20of%20Byju's.%20He%20co-founded%20the%20firm%20with%20Divya%20Gokulnath%2C%20a%20biotech%20engineer%20and%20former%20student%20whom%20he%20later%20married.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202015%2C%20Raveendran%20digitized%20his%20business%2C%20launching%20a%20self-learning%20app%20focused%20largely%20on%20math%2C%20science%20and%20English%20for%20primary%20school%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20always%20enjoyed%20learning%20things%20on%20my%20own%20and%20also%20taught%20myself%20to%20hack%20exams%2C%20so%20it%20was%20easy%20to%20tutor%20others%2C%26quot%3B%20Raveendran%20said%20in%20a%202017%20interview%20with%20Bloomberg%20News.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESurge%20in%20Cash%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20tech%20spending%20surged%20during%20the%20late%202010s%2C%20investors%20lined%20up%20to%20support%20Raveendran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERanjan%20Pai%2C%20who%20runs%20one%20of%20the%20nation's%20largest%20healthcare%20and%20education%20empires%2C%20said%20he%20agreed%20almost%20immediately%20to%20fund%20Byju's.%20Raveendran%20capitalized%20on%20a%20spike%20in%20internet%20usage%20in%20India.%20Companies%20like%20Reliance%20Jio%20Infocomm%20Ltd.%20introduced%20data%20tariffs%20that%20ranked%20among%20the%20most%20affordable%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20stands%20out%20as%20one%20of%20the%20brightest%20entrepreneurs%20in%20the%20country%20-%20yet%20is%20a%20teacher%20at%20heart%2C%26quot%3B%20Pai%20said%20in%20a%202017%20interview%20with%20Bloomberg.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20Byju's%20early%20backers%20was%20Sequoia%20Capital%2C%20which%20came%20aboard%20in%202015%20and%20invested%204.8%20billion%20rupees%20(%2458%20million)%2C%20according%20to%20data%20from%20Tracxn.%20Soon%20after%2C%20Lightspeed%20Venture%20Partners%20and%20the%20Chan%20Zuckerberg%20Initiative%20-%20the%20Facebook%20founder's%20philanthropic%20organization%20-%20participated%20in%20a%20%2450%20million%20funding%20round.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20capital%20flowed%20through%20the%20firm's%20accounts%2C%20Raveendran%20acquired%20more%20than%20a%20dozen%20educational%20companies%20in%20India%20and%20abroad.%20When%20the%20pandemic%20pushed%20students%20online%2C%20the%20buyouts%20seemed%20prescient.%20Raveendran%20planned%20to%20take%20the%20company%20public%20through%20a%20SPAC%20merger.%20Some%20investors%20offered%20valuations%20as%20high%20as%20%2448%20billion%2C%20according%20to%20documents%20reviewed%20by%20Bloomberg.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaveendran%20also%20tapped%20debt%20markets%20to%20fuel%20his%20acquisition%20spree.%20Though%20Byju's%20sought%20to%20borrow%20only%20%24500%20million%20in%202021%2C%20overseas%20investors%20-%20including%20Blackstone%20Inc.%2C%20Fidelity%20and%20GIC%20-%20put%20up%20enough%20cash%20to%20double%20the%20target%20size%20of%20the%20firm's%20term%20loan%20B%20to%20%241.2%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECracks%20in%20the%20Edifice%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20by%20the%20middle%20of%202022%2C%20problems%20began%20to%20compound.%20The%20SPAC%20boom%20petered%20out%2C%20along%20with%20demand%20for%20online%20tutoring.%20Employees%20questioned%20Raveendran's%20business%20instincts%3A%20Even%20as%20the%20lifting%20of%20Covid%20restrictions%20battered%20ed-tech%2C%20he%20sought%20to%20raise%20more%20equity%20-%20rather%20than%20conserve%20cash%20and%20target%20profitability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22ui9uj5uc%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fui9uj5uc_byju-losses-bloomberg-graphic_625x300_26_July_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20strategy%20hit%20a%20snag%20last%20July.%20Two%20key%20investors%2C%20Sumeru%20Ventures%20and%20Oxshott%2C%20failed%20to%20transfer%20about%20%24250%20million%20-%20part%20of%20the%20announced%20%24800%20million%20round%20-%20because%20of%20%26quot%3Bmacroeconomic%20reasons.%26quot%3B%20People%20familiar%20with%20the%20deal%20said%20Raveendran%20didn't%20verify%20whether%20the%20investors%20had%20enough%20money%20before%20announcing%20the%20deal.%20(The%20funds%20never%20came%20through.)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaveendran%20has%20avoided%20consulting%20investment%20bankers%20on%20deals%2C%20instead%20depending%20on%20Anita%20Kishore%2C%20his%20chief%20strategy%20officer%2C%20to%20execute%20most%20transactions%2C%20according%20to%20Byju's%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKishore%20and%20Raveendran%20declined%20to%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Indian%20officials%20sent%20queries%20to%20Byju's%20about%20why%20the%20firm%20couldn't%20close%20its%20financial%20accounts%20for%20the%20fiscal%20year%20ending%20March%202021.%20India's%20enforcement%20directorate%2C%20which%20investigates%20money%20laundering%20and%20forex%20violations%2C%20sent%20summons%20to%20company%20officials%2C%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECharges%20weren't%20filed%20against%20Byju's%20after%20the%20raid%20in%20late%20April.%20But%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Corporate%20Affairs%2C%20India's%20company%20regulator%2C%20will%20soon%20decide%20whether%20to%20open%20a%20formal%20probe%2C%20Bloomberg%20reported%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MCA%20and%20enforcement%20directorate%20didn't%20reply%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEighteen%20months%20after%20the%20financial%20year's%20close%2C%20Byju's%20finally%20released%20audited%20statements.%20They%20showed%20losses%20of%2045.7%20billion%20rupees%20-%20a%2013-fold%20jump%20from%20the%20previous%20year.%20Byju's%20blamed%20the%20performance%20on%20accounting%20practices%20that%20deferred%20revenue%20to%20subsequent%20years.%20Others%20pointed%20out%20a%20massive%20increase%20in%20marketing%20spending.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20firm's%20finances%20alarmed%20investors.%20Some%20creditors%2C%20including%20Blackstone%2C%20offloaded%20their%20holdings%2C%20giving%20distressed%20investors%20in%20the%20US%20a%20chance%20to%20pick%20up%20the%20%241.2%20billion%20loan%20at%20rates%20as%20low%20as%2064%20cents%20to%20a%20dollar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20buying%20the%20debt%2C%20those%20creditors%20began%20demanding%20accelerated%20payments%20as%20the%20firm%20had%20breached%20terms%2C%20including%20a%20September%20deadline%20for%20filing%20its%20results%20for%20the%20year%20ending%20March%2031%2C%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20eight%20months%20of%20negotiations%2C%20Byju's%20lenders%20in%20the%20US%20accused%20the%20firm%20in%20a%20Delaware%20lawsuit%20of%20hiding%20%24500%20million.%20They%20argued%20that%20Byju's%20is%20in%20technical%20default%20over%20the%20%241.2%20billion%20loan%20because%20the%20firm%20hasn't%20provided%20regular%20financial%20updates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22pchmqq3%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fpchmqq3_byju-loan-graphic-bloomberg_625x300_26_July_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20June%2C%20Byju's%20skipped%20a%20%2440%20million%20interest%20payment%20and%20filed%20its%20own%20lawsuit%20in%20New%20York%2C%20accusing%20the%20lenders%20of%20%26quot%3Bbad-faith%20negotiating.%26quot%3B%20The%20company%20has%20argued%20the%20debt%20contract%20prohibits%20lenders%20from%20selling%20their%20stakes%20to%20certain%20investors%2C%20including%20those%20who%20specialize%20in%20distressed%20debt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EShareholder%20Revolt%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20stakes%20continue%20to%20rise.%20Representatives%20from%20three%20big%20investors%20-%20Peak%20XV%2C%20Prosus%20and%20the%20Chan%20Zuckerberg%20Initiative%20-%20recently%20quit%20Byju's%20board.%20Deloitte%20Haskins%20%26amp%3B%20Sells%20also%20resigned%20as%20Byju's%20auditor%2C%20citing%20the%20firm's%20spotty%20financial%20records.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BByju's%20grew%20considerably%20since%20our%20first%20investment%20in%202018%2C%20but%2C%20over%20time%2C%20its%20reporting%20and%20governance%20structures%20did%20not%20evolve%20sufficiently%20for%20a%20company%20of%20that%20scale%2C%26quot%3B%20Prosus%20said%20in%20a%20July%2025%20statement%2C%20explaining%20why%20its%20director%20stepped%20down%20from%20Byju's%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20weeks%2C%20Raveendran%20and%20Ajay%20Goel%20-%20who%20joined%20Byju's%20in%20April%20as%20its%20chief%20financial%20officer%20-%20hired%20an%20affiliate%20of%20accounting%20firm%20BDO%20to%20take%20over%20auditing.%20Goel%20has%20said%20that%20long-delayed%20financial%20accounts%20will%20be%20finalized%20by%20the%20end%20of%20September.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20best%20of%20Byju's%20is%20yet%20to%20come%2C%26quot%3B%20Raveendran%20told%20employees%20at%20a%20recent%20town%20hall%2C%20where%20he%20pushed%20back%20on%20criticisms.%20The%20company%20has%20%26quot%3Bnot%20come%20this%20far%20to%20only%20come%20this%20far.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaveendran%20is%20counting%20on%20a%20%241%20billion%20equity%20investment%20from%20backers%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20which%20is%20expected%20as%20early%20as%20next%20month.%20He%20is%20also%20tapping%20some%20of%20his%20early%20backers%20in%20India%20to%20tide%20over%20the%20cash%20crunch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20funds%20come%20through%2C%20Byju's%20could%20pay%20down%20creditors%20and%20buy%20out%20the%20revolting%20US-based%20investors%2C%20according%20to%20people%20following%20the%20negotiations%2C%20who%20didn't%20want%20to%20be%20named%20because%20the%20discussions%20are%20private.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20earlier%20this%20week%2C%20lenders%20agreed%20to%20work%20toward%20restructuring%20the%20%241.2%20billion%20loan%20by%20Aug.%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20investors%20have%20slashed%20the%20firm's%20valuation%20to%20less%20than%20%2410%20billion.%20But%20despite%20Byju's%20rocky%20few%20months%2C%20many%20remain%20bullish%2C%20pointing%20to%20the%20firm's%20strong%20assets%2C%20including%20150%20million%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20company%20can%20still%20be%20brought%20back%20from%20th