rrendering%20to%20police%20with%20their%20nine-month-old%20baby%20in%20his%20arms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20police%2C%20Nazibur%2C%20a%20mechanical%20engineer%20by%20qualification%2C%20and%20Sanghamitra%20became%20friends%20on%20Facebook%20in%20June%202020%2C%20during%20the%20nationwide%20lockdown%20to%20contain%20the%20pandemic.%20Friendship%20turned%20to%20love%20within%20months%20and%20in%20October%20that%20year%2C%20the%20two%20eloped%20to%20Kolkata.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanghamitra's%20parents%20brought%20her%20back%20home%2C%20but%20she%20had%20already%20married%20Nazibur%20in%20a%20Kolkata%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20year%2C%20Sanghamitra's%20parents%20Sanjeev%20Ghosh%20and%20Junu%20Ghosh%20registered%20a%20police%20complaint%2C%20accusing%20her%20of%20theft.%20Sanghamitra%20was%20arrested%20and%20spent%20over%20a%20month%20in%20judicial%20custody.%20After%20getting%20bail%2C%20she%20returned%20to%20her%20parents'%20home%2C%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%202022%2C%20Sanghamitra%20and%20Nazibur%20eloped%20again%2C%20this%20time%20to%20Chennai%2C%20where%20they%20lived%20for%20five%20months.%20When%20the%20couple%20returned%20to%20Golaghat%20in%20August%2C%20Sanghamitra%20was%20pregnant.%20They%20started%20living%20at%20Nazibur's%20home%20and%20had%20a%20son%20last%20November%2C%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20four%20months%20later%2C%20in%20March%20this%20year%2C%20Sanghamitra%20left%20Nazibur's%20home%20with%20her%20infant%20son%20and%20went%20to%20her%20parents'%20home.%20She%20accused%20Nazibur%20of%20torturing%20her%20and%20registered%20a%20police%20complaint.%20A%20case%20of%20attempt%20to%20murder%20was%20registered%20and%20Nazibur%20was%20arrested.%20He%20was%20released%20on%20bail%20after%2028%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20out%20of%20the%20jail%2C%20Nazibur%20wanted%20to%20meet%20his%20child%2C%20but%20Sanghamitra's%20family%20did%20not%20let%20him.%20In%20fact%2C%20on%20April%2029%2C%20Nazibur's%20brother%20registered%20a%20police%20complaint%2C%20accusing%20Sanghamitra%20and%20her%20family%20members%20of%20assaulting%20Nazibur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%20afternoon%2C%20as%20tensions%20between%20the%20two%20sides%20reached%20a%20breaking%20point%2C%20Nazibur%20murdered%20his%20wife%20Sanghamitra%20and%20her%20parents.%20He%20then%20fled%20with%20his%20nine-month-old%20baby.%20Later%2C%20he%20surrendered%20before%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20Ghosh's%20home%2C%20the%20bodies%20of%20Sanghamitra%20and%20her%20parents%20lay%20in%20pools%20of%20blood%20oozing%20out%20of%20machete%20wounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20case%20of%20murder%20and%20house%20trespass%20has%20been%20registered%20against%20the%20accused%2C%26quot%3B%20Assam%20police%20chief%20GP%20Singh%20tweeted.%20The%20state%20CID%20team%20has%20been%20roped%20in%20to%20probe%20the%20grisly%20murder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForensic%20teams%20have%20also%20been%20called%20in%20and%20further%20investigation%20is%20on%2C%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690349760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fqp5tbnj_assam-murder_625x300_26_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhow-lockdown-love-story-ended-in-grisly-triple-murder-in-assam-4240391%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Covid%20lockdown%20love%20story%20has%20ended%20in%20a%20gruesome%20triple%20murder%20in%20Assam's%20Golaghat%20district.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhow-lockdown-love-story-ended-in-grisly-triple-murder-in-assam-4240391%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhow-lockdown-love-story-ended-in-grisly-triple-murder-in-assam-4240391%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhow-lockdown-love-story-end