ol-classes-vocational-coding-bagless-information-vid01%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENational%20Education%20Policy%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20laid%20great%20emphasis%20on%20inclusion%20in%20education%20that%20takes%20into%20consideration%20local%20contexts%20and%20diversity.%20The%20framework%20asserts%20that%20quality%20in%20the%20early%20childhood%20care%20ecosystem%20(ECCE)%20is%20the%20highest%20priority%2C%20as%20is%20the%20inclusion%20and%20equal%20participation%20of%20children%20with%20disabilities%20and%20those%20from%20economically%20disadvantaged%20groups.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20how%20do%20we%20extend%20the%20same%20future%20benefits%20to%20children%20with%20disabilities%2C%20who%20are%20disproportionately%20affected%20by%20an%20already%20fractured%20educational%20system%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20first%20programmes%20that%20the%20Foundation%20started%20was%20Karuna%20Vihar%2C%20an%20early%20childhood%20intervention%20centre%20that%20encourages%20the%20overall%20development%20of%20children%20between%20the%20ages%20of%200%20and%206%20by%20building%20on%20their%20strengths.%20Parents%20or%20guardians%20work%20closely%20with%20special%20educators%20and%20therapists%20so%20they%20can%20carry%20out%20the%20activities%20practised%20during%20lessons%20at%20home.%20They%20are%20also%20given%20counselling%20services%20and%20support%20group%20interventions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKaruna%20Vihar%20also%20focuses%20on%20%E2%80%98play%E2%80%99%20including%20theatre%20and%20creative%20interventions%20like%20exercises%20to%20help%20develop%20a%20child%E2%80%99s%20functional%20skills.%20They%20also%20involve%20play%20in%20developing%20individualised%20education%20plans%20for%20each%20child%20to%20learn%20speech%20and%20language%20skills%20and%20alternative%20communication%20systems%2C%20as%20well%20as%20encourage%20sensory%20stimulation%20and%20behaviour%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECrucial%20aspects%20of%20a%20person%E2%80%99s%20life%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERupa%20Bishnoi%2C%20director%20of%20diversity%20and%20inclusion%20at%20LRF%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20talk%20about%20%E2%80%98inclusive%20education%E2%80%99%2C%20we%20also%20mean%20their%20inclusion%20in%20society.%20We%20have%20two%20catchwords%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%98participation%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98opportunity%E2%80%99.%20I%20specifically%20work%20for%20the%20mainstreaming%20of%20our%20children%20with%20the%20kids%2C%20the%20parents%2C%20and%20the%20schools.%20The%20last%20one%20has%20been%20the%20most%20negligent%20so%20far.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20commonplace%20in%20India%20for%20school%20managements%20to%20deny%20opportunities%20to%20children%20with%20disabilities%20%E2%80%94%20sometimes%20due%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20understanding%2C%20and%20sometimes%20due%20to%20an%20unwillingness%20to%20%E2%80%9Ctake%20responsibility%E2%80%9D.%20Children%20may%20also%20face%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F302809%2Fanoushka-jolly-shark-tank-started-kavach-an-app-for-bullying%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebullying%20and%20discrimination%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20these%20institutions%2C%20often%20with%20limited%20intervention%20by%20school%20authorities.%20Then%20there%20is%20a%20lack%20of%20accessible%20and%20safe%20infrastructure%2C%20and%20special%20educators.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20work%20on%20a%20process%20where%20we%20contact%20schools%2C%20hold%20workshops%20with%20them%2C%20make%20them%20aware%20of%20different%20disabilities%2C%20establish%20relationships%E2%80%A6then%20we%20try%20to%20mainstream%20our%20children.%20For%20at%20least%20a%20year%20of%20support%2C%20we%20provide%20teachers%20with%20strategies%2C%20and%20work%20preventing%20the%20bullying%20of%20even%20parents%E2%80%A6This%20way%20we%E2%80%99ve%20managed%20to%20mainstream%20nine%20children%20in