s.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fpilot-whales-51-die-after-mass-stranding-on-beach-as-rescuers-battle-to-save-dozens-more-12927528%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fpilot-whales-51-die-after-mass-stranding-on-beach-as-rescuers-battle-to-save-dozens-more-12927528%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ban%20On%20Women's%20Beauty%20Salons%20In%20Afghanistan%20Comes%20Into%20Effect%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmid%20public%20protests%20and%20UN%20concern%2C%20the%20ban%20on%20women's%20beauty%20salons%20in%20Afghanistan%20came%20into%20effect%20on%20Tuesday%20following%20the%20deadline%20given%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Vice%20and%20Virtue%20on%20July%204%2C%20reported%20TOLO%20News.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaliban%2C%20in%20a%20new%20verbal%20decree%2C%20banned%20women's%20beauty%20salons%20in%20Kabul%20and%20other%20provinces%20across%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20order%2C%20women's%20beauty%20parlours%20in%20Afghanistan%20were%20no%20longer%20allowed%20to%20operate%20after%20July%2023%2C%20according%20to%20Khaama%20Press.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20Nations%20said%20that%20the%20forced%20closure%20of%20women's%20beauty%20salons%20could%20have%20a%20negative%20impact%20on%20the%20economy%20of%20women.%20The%20Deputy%20Spokesperson%20for%20the%20Secretary-General%20Farhan%20Haq%20also%20asked%20the%20Taliban%20authorities%20to%20halt%20the%20mandate%20of%20closing%20beauty%20salons%2C%20TOLO%20News%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Secretary-General%20supports%20the%20efforts%20by%20the%20UN%20Assistance%20Mission%20in%20Afghanistan%20(UNAMA)%2C%20which%20has%20called%20on%20the%20de%20facto%20authorities%20to%20halt%20the%20edict%20closing%20beauty%20salons.%20UNAMA%20has%20said%20that%20this%20restriction%20on%20women's%20rights%20will%20impact%20negatively%20on%20the%20economy%20and%20contradicts%20support%20for%20women's%20entrepreneurship%2C%20and%20we're%20seeking%20a%20reversal%20of%20the%20bans%2C%E2%80%9D%20Haq%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20beauty%20salon%20owners%20said%20that%20some%20of%20the%20women%20are%20the%20breadwinners%20for%20their%20families.%20Following%20the%20ban%2C%20they%20would%20not%20be%20able%20to%20support%20their%20families%2C%20TOLO%20News%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMastora%2C%20a%20beauty%20salon%20owner%20said%20that%20over%20ten%20other%20women%20in%20her%20salon%20financially%20support%20their%20families.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20shop%20is%20the%20sole%20means%20through%20which%20ten%20people%20support%20their%20families%20and%20are%20breadwinners%20of%20their%20families.%20They%20all%20come%20here%20because%20of%20problems%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Mastora.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHuma%2C%20another%20beauty%20salon%20owner%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BToday%20they%20took%20our%20bread%20and%20our%20work%20from%20us.%20We%20are%20very%20upset.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDays%20after%20the%20Taliban%20issued%20the%20decree%2C%20several%20women%20makeup%20artists%20protested%20against%20the%20move%2C%20urging%20that%20the%20order%20be%20rescinded%2C%20Tolo%20News%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20spokesperson%20of%20Kabul%20Municipality%20Nematullah%20Barakzai%2C%20women's%20beauty%20salons'%20business%20licenses%20will%20be%20invalid%20after%20the%20third%20of%20Asad%20(solar%20calendar)%20and%20they%20will%20not%20be%20permitted%20to%20operate%20until%20the%20following%20order%2C%20according%20to%20TOLO%20News.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20the%20third%20of%20Asad%2C%20these%20licenses%20will%20no%20longer%20be%20valid.%20In%20Kabul%2C%20only%20those%20classes%20are%20allowed%20to%20operate%20that%20have%20licenses%2C%E2%80%9D%20Barakzai%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20over%2012%2C000%20women's%20beauty%20salons%20across%20the%20country%2C%20with%20an%20average%20of%205%20women%20employed%20by%20each.%20There%20are%203%