s-sheikh-hasina-as-godda-plant-begins-power-export-to-bangladesh%2Farticle67084678.ece%5C%22%3Emet%20Bangladesh%20Prime%20Minister%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20in%20Dhaka%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20after%20power%20supply%20from%20the%20Group%E2%80%99s%20thermal%20power%20plant%20in%20Jharkhand%E2%80%99s%20Godda%20was%20kickstarted.%20The%20Godda%20USCTPP%20marked%20the%20Adani%20Group%E2%80%99s%20entry%20into%20transnational%20power%20projects.%20This%20is%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20commissioned%20transnational%20power%20project%20where%20100%25%20of%20the%20generated%20power%20is%20being%20supplied%20to%20another%20nation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fnumbers-suggest-bangladesh-didnt-need-the-adani-power-deal-so-why-was-it-signed%5C%22%3ENumbers%20Suggest%20Bangladesh%20Didn%E2%80%99t%20Need%20the%20Adani%20Power%20Deal.%20So%20Why%20Was%20it%20Signed%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EElectricity-bearing%20cables%20from%20Godda%20are%20passing%20through%20several%20areas%20of%20West%20Bengal%2C%20including%20Farakka%20in%20Murshidabad%20and%20Malda%2C%20before%20finally%20entering%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25165101%2FScreenshot-2023-07-25-at-4.44.53.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25165101%2FScreenshot-2023-07-25-at-4.44.53.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25165101%2FScreenshot-2023-07-25-at-4.44.53-300x195.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25165101%2FScreenshot-2023-07-25-at-4.44.53-1024x664.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-665011%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22778%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20Google%20Map%20depiction%20of%20the%20road%20route%20between%20Godda%20and%20Bangladesh%E2%80%99s%20Dhaka%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20such%20tower%2C%20supporting%20these%20cables%2C%20is%20at%20the%20mango%20and%20lychee%20orchard%20in%20the%20village%20of%20Beniyagram%20Imamnagar.%20It%20is%20in%20the%20construction%20of%20this%20tower%20in%202022%20that%20a%20story%20lies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGetting%20to%20Jafarganj%20Bazar%20in%20Beniyagram%20Imamnagar%2C%20via%20Benegram%20Dadantola%2C%20was%20a%20challenging%20task.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20route%20reflected%20the%20poverty%20of%20the%20place%2C%20with%20ramshackle%20houses%20and%20little%20by%20way%20of%20infrastructure.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWomen%20were%20seen%20working%20in%20the%20courtyards%2C%20tying%20%3Cem%3Ebidis%3C%2Fem%3E%20(hand-rolled%20cigarettes)%20into%20shape.%20All%20was%20calm%20when%20suddenly%2C%20startled%20by%20the%20presence%20of%20a%20stranger%20%E2%80%93%20this%20reporter%20%E2%80%93%20they%20began%20blowing%20loudly%20into%20their%20conch%20shells.%20The%20sound%20alerted%20everyone%20in%20the%20area%20and%20within%20minutes%20all%20the%20men%20had%20disappeared%20in%20an%20instant.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVillager%20Lutfar%20Rahman%2C%20the%20convener%20of%20Jeevan%20Jivika%20Bachao%20(%E2%80%98save%20lives%20and%20jobs%E2%80%99)%20Committee%2C%20later%20offered%20an%20inkling%20as%20to%20why%20there%20was%20such%20a%20reaction.%20Villagers%20fear%20police%20will%20arrive%20at%20their%20doorsteps%20with%20fabricated%20charges.%20Rahman%20himself%20is%20living%20elsewhere%2C%20because%20he%20feels%20he%20may%20be%20implicated%20in%20a%20case%20suddenly%20brought%20by%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%20is%20that%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20because%20villagers%20are%20engaged%20in%20a%20war%20of%20sorts%20with%20local%20law%20enforcement%2C%20who%20they%20allege%20are%20acting%20on%20the%20Adani%20Group%E2%80%99s%20behalf.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20was%20a%20while%20before%20local%20young%20men%2C%20realising%20this%20correspondent%20was%20not%20a%20threat%2C%20took%20me%20to%20the%20fruit%20orchard%20to%20tell%20me%20why%20they%20are%20suspicious%20of%20police%20and%20what%20this%20orchard%20has%20seen.%20The%20lights%20on%20the%20high-tension%20electric%20tower%20flickered%20in%20the%20distance.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25214914%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-25-at-5.12.11-PM.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25214914%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-25-at-5.12.11-PM.jpeg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25214914%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-25-at-5.12.11-PM-300x165.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25214914%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-25-at-5.12.11-PM-1024x564.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-665102%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22595%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20mango%20orchard%20at%20%3Cspan%3EBeniyagram%20Imamnagar%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3EMurshidabad.%20Photo%3A%20Joydeep%20Sarkar%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAsghar%20Sheikh%2C%20a%20local%2C%20began%20to%20speak%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Adani%20group%20acquired%20only%2016%20cottah%20of%20land%20here%20from%20two%20locals%2C%20Syed%20Ali%20Mushtaq%20and%20Israel.%20On%20it%2C%20they%20planned%20to%20construct%20the%20high-tension%20tower%20on%20that%20land.%20We%20realised%20immediately%20that%20this%20would%20result%20in%20the%20complete%20destruction%20of%20the%20mango%20orchard.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20price%20of%20this%20would%20be%20enormous.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CA%20mid-sized%20tree%20can%20give%20you%2030%2C000-35%2C000%20lychees.%20Even%20if%20the%20prices%20fall%20a%20lot%2C%20you%20can%20sell%20each%20fruit%20for%20at%20least%20Re%201.%20Our%20three-century-old%20lychee%20trees%20yield%20no%20fewer%20than%201%2C00%2C000-1%2C50%2C000%20lychees.%20These%20fruits%20are%20the%20most%20expensive%20in%20the%20state.%20All%20through%20the%20year%2C%20we%20look%20after%20the%20trees%2C%20irrigate%20the%20land%2C%20apply%20manure%20and%20spray%20insecticides.%20This%20is%20our%20job%20and%20our%20only%20livelihood%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sheikh.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Sheikh%20says%20that%20this%20fear%20compelled%20the%20village%20to%20oppose%20the%20construction.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20sought%20legal%20recourse%20by%20approaching%20the%20Calcutta%20high%20court.%20The%20court%20was%20scheduled%20to%20deliver%20its%20order%20on%20the%20matter%20on%20July%204%2C%202022.%20However%2C%20on%20July%202%2C%20they%20made%20a%20significant%20move%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sheikh%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWho%20were%20%E2%80%9Cthey%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWasim%20Khan%2C%20a%20local%20youth%2C%20said%20%E2%80%9Cthey%E2%80%9D%20were%20armed%20policemen%20and%20officials%20who%20arrived%20in%20the%20morning%20of%20July%202.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20318px)%2085vw%2C%20318px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25214922%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-25-at-5.12.12-PM.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22318%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25214922%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-25-at-5.12.12-PM.jpeg%20798w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25214922%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-25-at-5.12.12-PM-200x300.jpeg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25214922%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-25-at-5.12.12-PM-681x1024.jpeg%20681w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-665103%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22478%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EArmed%20security%20forces%20in%20the%20Murshidabad%20village%2C%20purportedly%20during%20the%20tower%20construction.%20Photo%3A%20By%20arrangement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlready%2C%20before%20July%202%2C%20more%20than%20150%20trees%20had%20been%20cut%20from%20the%20orchard%2C%20said%20locals.%20%3C%2Fspan%3EVillagers%20were%20thus%20suspicious%20of%20the%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20say%20that%20even%20before%20there%20could%20be%20any%20dialogue%2C%20policemen%20began%20beating%20up%20villagers%2C%20including%20women%20and%20children.%20Their%20homes%20were%20vandalised%20and%20nine%20women%20were%20severely%20injured.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20police%20and%20Adani%20swiftly%20occupied%20the%20deserted%20village%2C%20setting%20up%20camps%2C%E2%80%9D%20Khan%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20used%20machines%20to%20cut%20down%20the%20mahogany%2C%20mango%20and%20lychee%20trees%20and%20quickly%20loaded%20them%20onto%20trucks%2C%20probably%20to%20sell%20off%20the%20valuable%20timber%2C%20says%20Sheikh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20swiftly%20brought%20in%20generators%20and%20installed%20halogen%20lights%20so%20as%20to%20be%20able%20to%20quickly%20clear%20the%20entire%20orchard%20in%20an%20overnight%20operation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%20Sheikh%20says%20that%20the%20smell%20of%20sap%20still%20lingers%20from%20the%20oldest%20trees%20that%20were%20cut%20down.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20villager%20says%20that%20the%20tall%20tower%20which%20usually%20takes%20around%20a%20month%20to%20construct%20was%20built%20in%20three%20days.%20For%20those%20three%20days%2C%20none%20of%20the%20residents%20could%20return%20to%20the%20village.%20When%20police%20and%20Adani%20officials%20finally%20left%2C%20villagers%20who%20had%20sought%20refuge%20elsewhere%20began%20trickling%20back.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKhan%2C%20quoted%20earlier%2C%20says%20that%20shortly%20afterwards%2C%20at%20a%20time%20when%20many%20of%20the%20villagers%20were%20injured%20in%20the%20police%20beating%20and%20undergoing%20treatment%20at%20the%20Jangipur%20hospital%20nearby%2C%20a%20group%20of%20policemen%20arrived%20at%20the%20hospital%20and%20arrested%20them.%20They%20were%20kept%20in%20jail%20for%2016%20days%20before%20being%20let%20go%2C%20Khan%20claims.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20exercise%20took%20away%20the%20villagers%E2%80%99%20chance%20to%20reap%20a%20fruit%20crop%20this%20time%2C%20they%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKhan%20now%20works%20at%20a%20hotel%20in%20Goa%2C%20having%20realised%20after%20the%20lack%20of%20crops%20this%20year%20that%20life%20has%20a%20fruit%20cultivator%20will%20only%20get%20more%20difficult.%20There%20are%20many%20like%20him%2C%20he%20says%2C%20who%20are%20leaving%20the%20village%20to%20move%20to%20other%20states%20for%20better%20livelihood%20prospects.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERights%20organisation%20Manabadhikar%20Andolan%20member%20Sukanta%20Das%20says%20that%20had%20the%20high-tension%20wire%20passed%20over%20a%20smaller%20field%2C%20it%20would%20not%20have%20been%20as%20big%20a%20problem.%20Once%20power%20passes%20through%20these%20wires%2C%20trees%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20grow%20on%20its%20path.%20During%20storms%2C%20the%20danger%20of%20such%20wires%20getting%20ensnared%20in%20trees%20and%20snapping%20is%20a%20real%20one%20he%20says.%20%E2%80%9CI%20cannot%20understand%20why%20our%20state%20police%20is%20so%20eager%20to%20protect%20the%20interests%20of%20a%20private%20concern%20at%20such%20a%20cost%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20355px)%2085vw%2C%20355px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25214856%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-25-at-5.12.13-PM-1.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22355%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25214856%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-25-at-5.12.13-PM-1.jpeg%20963w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25214856%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-25-at-5.12.13-PM-1-241x300.jpeg%20241w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25214856%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-25-at-5.12.13-PM-1-822x1024.jpeg%20822w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-665100%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22443%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ECables%2C%20purportedly%20of%20Adani%20Power%2C%20going%20through%20the%20mango%20orchard%20in%20Murshidabad.%20Photo%3A%20Joydeep%20Sarkar%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20villages%20of%20Dadantola%2C%20Ballalpur%2C%20Kholakandi%2C%20and%20Samaspur%20have%20also%20seen%20similar%20scenes.%20In%20Dadantola%20too%2C%20a%20skirmish%20between%20villagers%20and%20police%20led%20to%20injuries%20on%20both%20sides.%20In%20all%20these%20villages%2C%20electric%20towers%20have%20been%20installed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20more%20villagers%20speak%20to%20this%20reporter%20on%20the%20situation%2C%20an%20elderly%20man%20asks%20why%20Didi%20%E2%80%93%20the%20term%20for%20elder%20sister%2C%20used%20for%20chief%20minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20%E2%80%93%20is%20not%20coming%20to%20their%20aid%20and%20why%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20in%20power%20at%20the%20centre%2C%20is%20missing%20too.%20%E2%80%9CWho%20is%20Adani%20to%20dictate%20our%20lives%3F%20Is%20there%20no%20justice%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20asks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELocals%20also%20raise%20the%20issue%20of%20a%20lack%20of%20effort%20on%20the%20state%20government%E2%80%99s%20part%20to%20fix%20compensation%20amounts.%20The%20average%20price%20of%20a%20cottah%20of%20land%20in%20and%20around%20the%20Dadantola%20area%20is%20Rs%205%20lakh.%20However%2C%20if%20that%20agricultural%20land%20is%20part%20of%20an%20orchard%2C%20the%20price%20could%20be%20even%20higher.%20Locals%20claim%20that%20more%20than%20500%20acres%20of%20land%20have%20been%20encroached%20upon%20for%20the%20electrical%20tower.%20One%20acre%20is%2032%20cottahs%20in%20Bengal%3B%20500%20would%20be%2016%2C000%20cottahs.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20key%20member%20of%20the%20corporate%20communication%20team%20from%20Adani%20Power%2C%20responsible%20for%20the%20Godda%20sector%2C%20spoke%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20over%20the%20phone%2C%20but%20did%20not%20address%20the%20charges%20of%20violence%20against%20villagers.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20matter%20is%20pending%20before%20the%20court.%20We%20will%20accept%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20verdict.%20We%20have%20accepted%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20verdict%20before%2C%20and%20this%20time%20will%20not%20be%20different.%20Electricity%20supply%20has%20already%20started%20in%20Bangladesh.%20We%20will%20abide%20by%20the%20law%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20what%20could%20the%20officials%20have%20done%20differently%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPrashant%20Nandi%20Chowdhury%2C%20a%20retired%20engineer%20of%20the%20West%20Bengal%20Power%20Development%20Corporation%2C%20with%20experience%20in%20power%20supply%20to%20remote%20areas%20through%20towers%2C%20says%20caution%20is%20key.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%9CDuring%20the%20construction%20of%20any%20power%20plant%2C%20it%20is%20necessary%20to%20conduct%20surveys%20in%20advance%20to%20identify%20a%20power%20supply%20route.%20If%20t