ace%20warps%20any%20surrounding%20people%20and%20buildings%20around%20its%20circumference%20like%20an%20all-consuming%20fun%20house%20mirror%20ball.%20It's%20almost%20hypnotic%20%E2%80%94%20imagine%20holding%20its%20gaze%20as%20the%20Orb%20affirms%20your%20humanity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20crypto%20paradise%20premise%20aside%2C%20Worldcoin%20has%20been%20tweeting%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-says-to-call-tweet-x-twitter-rebrand-2023-7%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAs%2520part%2520of%2520the%2520rebrand%2Cto%2520as%2520an%2520%2522x.%2522%5C%22%3E(or%20X'ing%3F)%3C%2Fa%3E%20photos%20of%20the%20objects%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20big%20cities.%20The%20choice%20to%20make%20it%20circular%20is%20interesting%20too%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Orb%20is%20the%20latest%20in%20the%20line%20of%20enigmatic%20orbs%20that%20have%20transfixed%20and%20disturbed%20observers%20on%20social%20media%2C%20like%20the%20beaming%20one%20Donald%20Trump%20was%20pictured%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2017%2F05%2F22%2Fworld%2Fmiddleeast%2Ftrump-glowing-orb-saudi.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eholding%20with%20world%20leaders%20back%20in%202017%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Worldcoin's%20Orbs%20look%20more%20like%20inscrutable%20machines%20than%20something%20mythological.%20One%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fworldcoin%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELisbon%20looks%20up%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20scenic%20portrait%20with%20the%20Bel%C3%A9m%20Tower.%20In%20Singapore%2C%20it%20shines%20in%20focus%20as%20the%20Marina%20Bay%20Sands%20hotel%20towers%20in%20the%20distance.%20There's%20an%20Orb%20flanked%20by%20palm%20trees%20in%20Miami%2C%20and%20another%20reflecting%20the%20sky%20in%20Tokyo.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221286%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Orb%20in%20Singapore.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3