C%20Mobile%20Internet%20Remains%20Suspended%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25202947%2FBetter-ethernet-cables.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Almost%20three%20months%20after%20it%20imposed%20a%20blanket%20internet%20ban%20on%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20residents%2C%20the%20Manipur%20government%20has%20decided%20to%20allow%20broadband%20internet%20access%20with%20strict%20conditions%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20July%2025.%20The%20government%20has%20kept%20mobile%20internet%20services%20suspended.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubject%20to%20a%20list%20of%20conditions%2C%20including%20having%20to%20submit%20a%20signed%20undertaking%20to%20one%E2%80%99s%20internet%20service%20provider%20(ISP)%2C%20people%20with%20subscriptions%20to%20internet%20lease%20line%20(ILL)%20and%20fibre-to-the-home%20(FTTH)%20broadband%20connections%20have%20been%20allowed%20internet%20access.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EILL%20connections%20are%20typically%20used%20by%20large%20organisations%2C%20including%20businesses%20and%20government%20institutions.%20FTTH%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20is%20usually%20availed%20by%20households%20and%20individual%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20even%20those%20with%20broadband%20internet%20connections%20will%20have%20to%20adhere%20to%20a%20host%20of%20conditions%2C%20including%20the%20blocking%20of%20social%20media%20websites.%20Other%20conditions%20placed%20on%20the%20restoration%20of%20broadband%20internet%20include%20having%20to%20use%20static%20IP%20addresses%2C%20not%20using%20virtual%20private%20networks%20(VPNs)%20or%20accessing%20the%20web%20through%20Wi-Fi%20connections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20any%20of%20the%20restrictions%20are%20violated%2C%20action%20will%20be%20taken%20against%20the%20person%20who%20gave%20the%20undertaking%20%E2%80%9Cunder%20relevant%20laws%E2%80%9D.%20Even%20if%20a%20secondary%20user%20violates%20the%20restrictions%2C%20the%20person%20who%20signed%20the%20undertaking%20will%20be%20liable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Manipur%20home%20department%20justified%20the%20continued%20ban%20on%20mobile%20internet%20because%20its%20%E2%80%9Cpreparedness%20for%20having%20%5Ban%5D%20effective%20control%20and%20regulatory%20mechanism%E2%80%9D%20for%20these%20services%20%E2%80%9Cis%20not%20technically%20feasible.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20order%20continued%20to%20say%20that%20control%20mechanisms%20were%20%E2%80%9Cstill%20poor%E2%80%9D%20to%20prevent%20the%20loss%20of%20lives%20and%20damage%20to%20property%20caused%20by%20the%20spread%20of%20disinformation%20and%20rumours%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwe-cant-look-away-from-internet-shutdowns-in-manipur%5C%22%3EWe%20Can%E2%80%99t%20Look%20Away%20From%20Internet%20Shutdowns%20in%20Manipur%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ET.%20Ranjit%20Singh%2C%20the%20home%20department%E2%80%99s%20commissioner%2C%20acknowledged%20the%20suffering%20its%2082-day-long%20internet%20ban%20had%20caused%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20residents%20in%20his%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20state%20government%20has%20reviewed%20the%20issues%20of%20the%20ban%20on%20internet%20since%20May%203%2C%202023%20continuously%20without%20any%20break%20(except%20%5Bin%5D%20exempted%20cases)%20and%20considered%20the%20suffering%20of%20the%20Common%20%5Bsic%5D%20as%20the%20internet%20ban%20had%20affected%20important%20offices%2Finstitutions%2C%20cohort%20of%20people%20on%20%5Ba%5D%20work%20from%20home%20basis%2C%20chartered%20accountant%20firms%2C%20lawyers%2C%20health%20facilities%2C%20refuelling%20centres%2C%20recharging%20of%20electricity%2Fmobile%2C%20booking%20for%20LPG%2C%20educational%20institutions%2C%20taxation-related%20offices%2C%20other%20online-based%20citizen-centric%20services%20etc.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20strict%20conditions%20imposed%20on%20internet%20usage%20have%20come%20under%20criticism%20for%20having%20too%20narrow%20a%20scope.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdvocate%20and%20public%20policy%20professional%20Apar%20Gupta%20tweeted%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20the%20conditional%20lift%20of%20the%20ban%20applies%20only%20to%20a%20%E2%80%9Csmall%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cnegligible%E2%80%9D%20number%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20total%20internet%20users%20and%20should%20not%20be%20characterised%20as%20partial%20restoration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWireline%20will%20prefer%20institutional%20and%20users%20on%20higher%20income%20groups%20that%20comprise%20a%20%E2%80%98tiny%E2%80%99%20number%20of%20users%20of%20the%20total%20pie.%20Even%20for%20them%20severe%20restrictions%20include%20banning%20WiFi%20hotspots%2C%20social%20media%2C%20VPNs%2C%E2%80%9D%20his%20tweet%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20my%20firm%20belief%20the%20internet%20shutdown%20is%20to%20serve%20state%20interests%20in%20avoiding%20accountability%20and%20contouring%20the%20media%20ecology%20than%20any%20evidentiary%20law%20and%20order%20objective.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThe%20State%20Government%20of%20Manipur%20has%20reportedly%20%E2%80%9Clifted%E2%80%9D%20the%20Internet%20Shutdown%20in%20Manipur.%20I%20would%20urge%20journalists%20to%20scrutinise%20this%20claim%20especially%20how%20they%20craft%20their%20headlines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20internet%20has%20not%20been%20%E2%80%9Cpartially%E2%80%9D%20lifted%20but%20to%20a%2C%20%E2%80%9Csmall%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cnegligible%E2%80%9D%20number%20of%20users%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FdigOwYj1mq%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FdigOwYj1mq%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Apar%20(%40apar1984)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fapar1984%2Fstatus%2F1683798197649682433%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2025%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20the%20dubious%20distinction%20of%20being%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Findia-remains-internet-shutdown-capital-of-the-world-for-fifth-year-running-report%5C%22%3Einternet%20shutdown%20capital%20of%20the%20world%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20clocking%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20such%20shutdowns%20by%20any%20democracy%20for%20the%20fifth%20consecutive%20year%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Manipur%20government%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20allow%20restricted%20internet%20access%20comes%20after%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20high%20court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmanipur-internet-ban-supreme-court%5C%22%3Edirected%20it%20twice%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20consider%20doing%20so%20in%20a%20conditional%20manner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ban%20was%20imposed%20on%20May%203%2C%20when%20violence%20between%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20Meitei%20and%20Kuki%20communities%20erupted%20and%20has%20been%20ongoing.%20At%20least%20150%20people%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20the%20violence%20and%20over%2060%2C000%20others%20have%20been%20displaced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInternet%20bans%20were%20periodically%20extended%20by%20the%20government%20ever%20since%20and%20seemed%20to%20be%20effectively%20indefinite.%20The%20bans%20have%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Famnesty-alarm-manipur-violence-peace%5C%22%3Ecriticised%20for%20being%20overly%20broad%20in%20degree%20and%20scope%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20home%20department%E2%80%99s%20order%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20sample%20undertaking%20to%20be%20signed%20by%20residents%20for%20internet%20access%2C%20have%20been%20reproduced%20below.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scribd.com%2Fembeds%2F661088287%2Fcontent%3Fstart_page%3D1%26view_mode%3Dscroll%26access_key%3Dkey-EztlMsd29UgKq0ZBUYsp%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20data-auto-height%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20data-aspect-ratio%3D%