reply%20to%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20the%20minister%20for%20information%20and%20broadcasting%2C%20Anurag%20Singh%20Thakur%2C%20said%20that%20four%20influencer%20marketing%20agencies%20have%20been%20empanelled%20for%20wider%20dissemination%20of%20government%20schemes%20and%20campaigns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMinistry%20of%20Electronic%20and%20Information%20Technology%20(MeitY)%20has%20informed%20that%20MyGov%20has%20in%20March%202023%20undertaken%20a%20process%20for%20empanelment%20of%20influencer%20marketing%20agencies%20with%20an%20objective%20of%20enabling%20wider%20dissemination%20and%20enhance%20citizen%20engagement%20in%20respect%20of%20information%20related%20to%20various%20schemes%2Fcampaigns%2Finitiatives%20of%20Government%20of%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Thakur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBased%20on%20the%20response%20to%20the%20bid%2C%20MyGov%20has%20empanelled%20four%20agencies.%20No%20amount%20has%20been%20spent%20under%20the%20said%20empanelment%20process%20till%20date.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fquestions-over-financing-of-union-ministers-interviews-with-youtube-influencers%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20a%20series%20of%20interviews%20with%20Union%20ministers%20conducted%20by%20social%20media%20influencers%20in%20collaboration%20with%20MyGov%20have%20raised%20questions%20about%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20use%20of%20public%20funds%20to%20finance%20these%20interactions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fquestions-over-financing-of-union-ministers-interviews-with-youtube-influencers%5C%22%3EQuestions%20Over%20Financing%20of%20Union%20Ministers%E2%80%99%20Interviews%20With%20YouTube%20Influencers%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYouTube%20influencers%20like%20Ranveer%20Allahabadia%20conducted%20interviews%20with%20Union%20ministers%20Rajeev%20Chandrashekhar%2C%20Union%20Minister%20of%20State%20for%20Entrepreneurship%2C%20Skill%20Development%2C%20Electronics%20%26amp%3B%20Technology%3B%20Dr%20S.%20Jaishankar%2C%20Union%20Minister%20for%20External%20Affairs%3B%20and%20Commerce%20and%20Industry%20Minister%20Piyush%20Goyal%20for%20his%20YouTube%20channel%20Beer%20Biceps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20YouTube%20influencer%20Raj%20Shamani%20has%20also%20uploaded%20similar%20exclusive%20interviews%20on%20his%20YouTube%20channel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20influencers%E2%80%99%20interviews%20include%20the%20phrase%20%E2%80%9Cin%20collaboration%20with%20MyGov%E2%80%9D%20in%20their%20description%20boxes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShamani%20had%20also%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20interactions%20were%20a%20%E2%80%9Cvoluntary%2C%20unpaid%20partnership%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%20the%20Union%20government%20also%20published%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsuchetadalal%2Fstatus%2F1673185032884854784%5C%22%3Efront-page%20advertisements%20in%20prominent%20newspapers%3C%2Fa%3E%20endorsing%20some%20select%20social%20media%20influencers%2C%20with%20their%20images%20and%20the%20mention%20of%20their%20YouTube%20channels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ministry%20of%20Electronics%20and%20Information%20and%20Technology%20(MeitY)%20on%20March%207%20released%20a%20tender%20inviting%20proposals%20for%20the%20empanelment%20of%20various%20Agencies%20(Social%20Media%20Marketing%20Agencies)%20handling%20Influencer%20Marketing%20or%20specialised%20Influencer%20Marketing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThakur%20told%20the%20parliament%20that%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Communications%20(CBC)%2C%20under%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Information%20and%20Broadcasting%2C%20undertakes%20campaigns%20relating%20to%20publicity%2Fawareness%20generation%20of%20programmes%2F%20schemes%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20this%20purpose%2C%20the%20CBC%20has%20in%20place%20transparent%20Policy%20Guidelines%20for%20empanelment%20of%20media%2Fagencies%20and%20release%20of%20advertisements%20and%20other%20promotions%20on%20media%20platforms%2C%20including%20for%20digital%20media%2Fsocial%20media%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20concerns%20have%20been%20raised%20about%20the%20use%20of%20these%20influencer%20interactions%20to%20influence%20opinions%20ahead%20of%20the%20general%20elections%20in%202024.%20Earlier%20this%20month%2C%20the%20Congress%20had%20shared%20a%20finance%20ministry%20order%20from%20May%20and%20accused%20the%C2%A0%20Modi%20government%20of%20%E2%80%9Cundermining%20the%20sanctity%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20Budget%20by%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcongress-centre-usurping-publicity-funds-ministries-own-use%5C%22%3Eusurping%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%2040%25%20of%20funds%20allocated%20to%20various%20ministries%20for%20publicity%20and%20handing%20it%20to%20the%20CBC.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690296650000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F26204048%2FUnion-ministers-S.-Jaishankar-Piyush-Goyal-among-others-have-appeared-on-these-YouTube-channels-for-interviews-which-are-in-collaboration-with-MyGov.-However-there-is-opaqueness-with-regard-to-terms-of.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fno-money-spent-on-union-ministers-interviews-with-social-media-influencers-govt-tells-parliament%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20controversy%2C%20Union%20minister%20Anurag%20Singh%20Thakur%20said%20that%20four%20influencer%20marketing%20agencies%20have%20been%20empanelled%20for%20wider%20dissemination%20of%20government%20schemes%20and%20campaigns%20in%20a%20written%20reply%20to%20Lok%20Sabha.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fno-money-spent-on-union-ministers-interviews-with-social-media-influencers-govt-tells-parliament%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Lok%20Sabha%20Passes%20Biological%20Diversity%20Amendment%20Bill%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25193917%2FScreenshot-2023-07-25-at-7.38.21-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20On%20Tuesday%2C%20July%2025%2C%20amid%20the%20opposition%E2%80%99s%20loud%20protests%20on%20the%20violence%20in%20Manipur%2C%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20passed%20the%20Biological%20Diversity%20(Amendment%20Bill)%2C%202021%2C%20by%20a%20voice%20vote.%20The%20Bill%20brings%20changes%20to%20the%20Biological%20Diversity%20Act%2C%202002%20by%20decriminalising%20biodiversity%20offences%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmong%20the%20many%20criticisms%20of%20the%20Bill%20was%20that%20it%20promotes%20%E2%80%98ease%20of%20doing%20business%E2%80%99%20and%20would%20exempt%20users%20of%20codified%20traditional%20knowledge%20and%20Ayurveda%2C%20Yoga%20and%20Naturopathy%2C%20Unani%2C%20Siddha%2C%20and%20Homoeopathy%20(AYUSH)%20practitioners%20from%20sharing%20benefits%20with%20local%20communities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ELok%20Sabha%20passes%20Bill%20by%20voice%20vote%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnion%20environment%20minister%20Bhupender%20Yadav%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20discussed%20the%20Biological%20Diversity%20(Amendment%20Bill)%2C%202021%2C%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20July%2025.%20Today%2C%20a%20%E2%80%9Csignificant%E2%80%9D%20Bill%20is%20being%20discussed%20in%20this%20house%2C%20Yadav%20said.%20He%20added%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%E2%80%98Significant%E2%80%99%20because%20the%20whole%20world%20is%20undergoing%20a%20triple%20crisis%20now.%20On%20one%20side%20is%20the%20crisis%20of%20climate%20change%2C%20on%20another%20is%20the%20crisis%20of%20desertification%20of%20land%2C%20and%20on%20the%20third%2C%20the%20crisis%20of%20the%20loss%20of%20biological%20resources.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20our%20country%2C%20we%20want%20to%20promote%20ease%20of%20doing%20business%E2%80%A6by%20%5Bdecriminalising%20offences%5D%20ease%20of%20doing%20business%20and%20ease%20of%20living%20is%20being%20brought%20forward%20by%20this%20Bill%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20minister%20spoke%20right%20through%20loud%20protests%20%E2%80%93%20by%20the%20opposition%20pertaining%20to%20the%20ethnic%20conflict%20in%20Manipur%20%E2%80%93%20in%20the%20background.%20The%20Bill%20was%20passed%20by%20voice%20vote%20later%20and%20the%20House%20adjourned%20till%205%20pm%20immediately%20after%20the%20passage%20of%20the%20Bill.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20Biological%20Diversity%20Amendment%20Bill%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Bill%20will%20amend%20the%20Biological%20Diversity%20Act%2C%202002%2C%20which%20provides%20for%20the%20conservation%20of%20biological%20diversity%20in%20India%20and%20their%20sustainable%20use%2C%20as%20well%20as%20fair%20and%20equitable%20sharing%20of%20the%20benefits%20that%20arise%20from%20using%20biodiversity.%20It%20was%20first%20introduced%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20December%2016%2C%202021%2C%20by%20Yadav.%20Experts%20have%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscience.thewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fbiodiversity-amendments-further-isolate-agriculture-environment-ministries%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eargued%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20Bill%20encourages%20a%20conducive%20environment%20for%20investments%20%E2%80%93%20promotes%20%E2%80%9Cease%20of%20doing%20business%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20and%20simplifies%20the%20patent%20application%20process%2C%20and%20that%20it%20will%20further%20alienate%20India%E2%80%99s%20agriculture%20and%20environment%20ministries.%20There%20has%20also%20been%20concern%20that%20the%20Bill%20will%20exempt%20users%20of%20codified%20traditional%20knowledge%20and%20AYUSH%20practitioners%20from%20sharing%20benefits%20with%20local%20communities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Bill%2C%20following%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fvidhilegalpolicy.in%2Fresearch%2Fcomments-to-the-joint-committee-on-parliament-on-the-biological-diversity-amendment-bill-2021%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecriticisms%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20was%20referred%20to%20a%20Joint%20Parliamentary%20Committee%20chaired%20by%20Sanjay%20Jaiswal.%20The%20committee%E2%80%99s%20report%20was%20tabled%20in%20Parliament%20on%20August%202%2C%202022.%20Some%20experts%20have%20said%20that%20the%20committee%20has%20addressed%20several%20points%20raised%20by%20critics.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-conversation%3D%5C%22none%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EOur%20major%20submission%20was%20reg.%20the%20ambiguous%20definition%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cforeign%20controlled%20company%E2%80%9D%20which%20would%20have%20changed%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20Act%20altogether.%20Glad%20that%20the%20report%20not%20just%20discusses%20this%20point%20but%20accepting%20our%20suggestion%20of%20S2(27)%20of%20the%20Companies%20Act.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FR8t42n0Wvj%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FR8t42n0Wvj%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Debadityo%20Sinha%20(%40debadityo)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdebadityo%2Fstatus%2F1554507332603691008%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%202%2C%202022%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20the%20committee%20accepted%20several%20amendments%20%E2%80%93%20including%20ones%20that%20exempt%20users%20of%20codified%20traditional%20knowledge%20from%20sharing%20benefits%20with%20local%20communities%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fbiological-diversity-bill-passed-amid-opposition-protests-on-manipur-violence-101690279400291.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20instance%2C%20experts%20had%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fvidhilegalpolicy.in%2Fresearch%2Fcomments-to-the-joint-committee-on-parliament-on-the-biological-diversity-amendment-bill-2021%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eraised%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20concerns%20about%20the%20Bill%20decriminalising%20offences%20under%20the%20Act%20and%20making%20them%20punishable%20only%20with%20a%20penalty%20(between%20Rs%201%20lakh%20and%20Rs%2050%20lakh%20and%20continuing%20violations%20can%20attract%20an%20additional%20penalty%20of%20up%20to%20Rs%201%20crore)%20and%20no%20imprisonment.%20The%20committee%20merely%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fprsindia.org%2Fbilltrack%2Fprs-products%2Fjpc-report-summary%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520Bill%2520was%2520introduced%2520in%2Cassociated%2520knowledge%2520with%2520local%2520communities.%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eobserved%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20penalty%20structure%20should%20not%20be%20too%20meagre%20as%20it%20could%20enable%20violators%20to%20escape%20with%20a%20small%20fine.%20It%20recommended%20that%20the%20penalty%20should%20be%20proportionate%20to%20the%20gains%20obtained%20by%20entities%20and%20the%20size%20of%20the%20company.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690294840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25193917%2FScreenshot-2023-07-25-at-7.38.21-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Flok-sabha-passes-biological-diversity-amendment-bill%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Bill%20was%20cleared%20amidst%20loud%20protests%20by%20the%20opposition%20regarding%20the%20violence%20in%20Manipur.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%2