E%3Cspan%3EThese%20instances%20draw%20attention%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20while%20Modi%20and%20the%20entire%20rank%20and%20file%20of%20the%20ruling%20party%20never%20miss%20an%20opportunity%20to%20take%20credit%2C%20they%20shy%20away%20from%20taking%20responsibility.%20Hearts%20that%20were%20beating%20fast%20while%20cheering%20another%20instance%20of%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20political%20tokenism%2C%20remain%20silent%20at%20the%20turn%20of%20events%20in%20Manipur%20over%20almost%20three%20months.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F06%2F22174705%2F5782941.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221100%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F06%2F22174705%2F5782941.jpg%201100w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F06%2F22174705%2F5782941-300x150.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F06%2F22174705%2F5782941-1024x511.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F06%2F22174705%2F5782941-800x400.jpg%20800w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-603145%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22549%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EBJP%20Presidential%20candidate%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%20Photo%3A%20pmindia.gov.in%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EModi%20downward%2C%20every%20BJP%20leader%20could%20only%20be%20expected%20to%20act%20the%20way%20they%20have%20%E2%80%93%20that%20is%20of%20looking%20at%20every%20issue%20from%20a%20majoritarian%20and%20electoral%20perspective.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20one%20expected%20President%20Murmu%20would%20have%20been%20truer%20to%20her%20office%20than%20she%20has%20been%20by%20her%20silence.%20In%20the%20absence%20of%20any%20other%20reaction%20from%20her%2C%20this%20can%20only%20be%20taken%20as%20tacit%20endorsement%20of%20violent%20events%20in%20the%20northeastern%20border%20state.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EParadoxically%2C%20her%20office%20does%20not%20limit%20the%20Rashtrapati%E2%80%99s%20powers%20nor%20dictates%20that%20she%20acts%20only%20at%20the%20direction%20of%20the%20government%20and%20within%20it%2C%20the%20all-powerful%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20Office.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20president%20is%20in%20fact%2C%20not%20just%20an%20all-abiding%20titular%20head%2C%20but%20has%20the%20capacity%20to%20act%20on%20her%20own.%20The%20decision%20to%20act%20or%20not%20is%20however%20the%20president%E2%80%99s.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20President%20Murmu%E2%80%99s%20choice%20if%20she%20wants%20to%20be%20recalled%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98rubber%20stamp%E2%80%99%20president%20like%20many%20who%20preceded%20her%2C%20including%20immediate%20predecessor%20Ram%20Nath%20Kovind%2C%20or%20if%20she%20wishes%20to%20follow%20in%20the%20footsteps%20of%20more%20independent-minded%20presidents%20like%20K.R.%20Narayanan%20and%20A.P.J.%20Abdul%20Kalam.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20similarities%20between%20Murmu%20and%20Abdul%20Kalam%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOf%20the%20two%2C%20it%20is%20more%20contextual%20now%20to%20recall%20the%20independent%20and%20all-inclusive%20nature%20of%20the%20president%E2%80%99s%20office%20as%20underscored%20by%20Kalam.%20There%20are%20at%20least%20two%20counts%20on%20which%20there%20are%20obvious%20parallels%20between%20his%20tenure%20and%20President%20Murmu%E2%80%99s%20stay%20in%20this%20office.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFirstly%2C%20like%20President%20Murmu%2C%20Kalam%20too%20was%20a%20nominee%20of%20the%20BJP%20%E2%80%93%20although%20the%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20government%20secured%20the%20support%20of%20several%20parties%20in%20the%20opposition%20for%20Kalam%E2%80%99s%20candidature.%20Despite%20this%2C%20there%20is%20no%20denying%20that%20the%20scientist%20turned%20first%20citizen%20was%20principally%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20choice%20because%20it%20previously%20shot%20down%20the%20proposal%20of%20elevating%20vice%20president%20Krishna%20Kant%20as%20the%20president%20after%20considering%20his%20candidature.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20second%20similarity%20between%20Kalam%E2%80%99s%20time%20in%20office%20and%20that%20of%20President%20Murmu%E2%80%99s%20is%20of%20greater%20relevance%20in%20the%20current%20context.%20Kalam%2C%20it%20needs%20to%20be%20recalled%2C%20assumed%20office%20on%20the%20same%20date%20but%20in%202002.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20Kalam%20assumed%20office%2C%20it%20had%20not%20even%20been%20six%20months%20since%20the%20morbid%20Gujarat%20riots.%20At%20that%20time%2C%20the%20country%20was%20rife%20with%20accusations%20of%20the%20state%20government%2C%20headed%20by%20Modi%20as%20chief%20minister%2C%20being%20complicit%20in%20the%20violence.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDemands%20for%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20resignation%20still%20rent%20the%20air%20even%20though%20Vajpayee%2C%20who%20wanted%20him%20to%20quit%2C%20had%20been%20isolated%20within%20the%20party%20by%20the%20group%20led%20by%20home%20minister%20Lal%20Krishna%20Advani.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20that%20surcharged%20atmosphere%2C%20Kalam%20decided%20to%20make%20Gujarat%20the%20first%20port%20of%20call%20after%20assuming%20office.%20The%20day-long%20visit%20was%20scheduled%20for%20August%2012%2C%20barely%20two%20days%20prior%20to%20his%20first%20address%20to%20the%20nation%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20Independence%20Day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20visit%20was%20important%20for%20two%20more%20reasons.%20One%2C%20that%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20presidential%20election%2C%20he%20had%20been%20queried%20about%20his%20position%20on%20communal%20violence%2C%20the%20central%20domestic%20issue%20in%20the%20country%20at%20that%20time.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETwo%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20had%20dissolved%20the%20state%20assembly%20on%20July%2019%20and%20was%20demanding%20early%20elections%20against%20the%20opinion%20of%20the%20opposition%20%E2%80%93%20and%20more%20importantly%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20headed%20by%20J.M.%20Lyngdoh%2C%20who%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Fatal-ticks-off-modi-for-lyngdoh-slander%2Fcid%2F870282%5C%22%3Etargeted%20by%20Modi%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20his%20religious%20identity.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWithout%20a%20doubt%2C%20Kalam%E2%80%99s%20visit%20at%20the%20time%20was%20upsetting%20for%20the%20Vajpayee%20government.%20Yet%20he%20went%20ahead%20with%20his%20plans.%20In%20his%20memoirs%20of%20the%20presidency%2C%20%3Cem%3ETurning%20Points%3A%20A%20Journey%20Through%20Challenges%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20he%20mentioned%20that%20%E2%80%9Cat%20the%20ministry%20and%20bureaucratic%20level%2C%20it%20was%20suggested%20that%20I%20should%20not%20venture%20into%20Gujarat%20at%20that%20point%20of%20time.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFurther%2C%20he%20wrote%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CPM%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20was%20discomfited%20by%20my%20decision.%20He%20asked%20me%2C%20%E2%80%98Do%20you%20consider%20going%20to%20Gujarat%20at%20this%20time%20essential%E2%80%99%3F%20I%20replied%2C%20%E2%80%98I%20must%20go%20and%20talk%20to%20the%20people%20as%20a%20President.%20I%20consider%20this%20my%20first%20major%20task%E2%80%99.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETalk%20to%20the%20people%2C%20Kalam%20indeed%20did%2C%20almost%20as%20a%20curtain-raiser%20to%20his%20acts%20through%20the%20tenure%20which%20gave%20conferred%20on%20him%20the%20moniker%20of%20%E2%80%98People%E2%80%99s%20President%E2%80%99.%20He%20toured%20the%20suburb%20of%20Naroda%20Patia%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20Ahmedabad%20and%20the%20site%20of%20the%20worst%20carnage%20targeting%20Muslim%20residents%20during%20the%20riots.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPhotographs%20of%20an%20anguished%20First%20Citizen%20listening%20to%20a%20young%20survivor%20in%20the%20locality%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fkalam-the-president-went-where-his-conscience-took-him%5C%22%3Eabound%20the%20Internet%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20underscoring%20that%20the%20president%20can%20act%20on%20her%20or%20his%20own%20volition%20and%20need%20not%20limit%20to%20merely%20for-the-record%20events.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F07%2Fkalam-at-naroda-patiya.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22691%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F07%2Fkalam-at-naroda-patiya.jpg%20588w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F07%2Fkalam-at-naroda-patiya-300x219.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-7568%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22505%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAPJ%20Abdul%20Kalam%20listens%20to%20a%20young%20survivor%20at%20Naroda%20Patiya%2C%20Ahmedabad%2C%20the%20site%20of%20one%20of%20the%20worst%20incidents%20during%20the%202002%20Gujarat%20riots%2C%20during%20his%20visit%20to%20the%20state%20in%20August%202002.%20Photo%3A%20PTI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKalam%E2%80%99s%20visit%20forced%20Modi%20to%20go%20to%20the%20site%20of%20one%20of%20the%20most%20horrific%20carnages%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20However%2C%20even%20though%20the%20chief%20minister%20accompanied%20Kalam%2C%20the%20state%20administration%20%E2%80%98sanitised%E2%80%99%20the%20city%20and%20removed%20every%20visible%20sign%20of%20destruction.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBurnt%20vehicles%20and%20rubble%20of%20destroyed%20houses%20were%20removed%20while%20charred%20homes%20were%20painted%20afresh%20and%20roads%20were%20hastily%20paved.%20Kalam%20as%20president%20did%20not%20politicise%20his%20visit%20and%20did%20not%20deliver%20a%20sermon%20to%20Modi%20like%20Vajpayee%20in%20April%202002%20%E2%80%93%20when%20he%20made%20the%20famous%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fvajpayee-was-a-prime-minister-who-knew-the-limits-and-responsibilities-of-power%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CRaj%20Dharma%E2%80%9D%20statement%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20president%20Kalam%E2%80%99s%20visit%20underscored%20that%20all%20was%20not%20yet%20well%20with%20Gujarat.%20The%20visit%20added%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Felection-commission-jm-lyngodh-modi-model-code%5C%22%3Ecourage%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%20to%20not%20hold%20elections%20before%20October%2C%20as%20demanded%20by%20Modi%20and%20his%20government.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Eventually%2C%20the%20matter%20reached%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20after%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.tribuneindia.com%2F2002%2F20020821%2Fmain1.htm%5C%22%3EPresidential%20Reference%20was%20made%20to%20it%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPresident%20Kalam%20was%20no%20troublemaker%2C%20although%20he%20disagreed%20with%20the%20UPA%20government%20too%20on%20the%20Office%20of%20Profit%20issue.%20He%20clearly%20followed%20his%20own%20conscience%20while%20abiding%20by%20the%20oath%20of%20his%20office%20(and%20that%20of%20the%20governor%20too)%2C%20which%20is%20different%20from%20that%20of%20the%20prime%20minister%20and%20others%20holding%20elected%20posts.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EK.R.%20Narayanan%20and%20%E2%80%98indirect%20influence%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20fact%2C%20it%20was%20President%20Narayanan%20who%20on%20assuming%20office%2C%20comprehended%20the%20weight%20of%20the%20oath%20and%20realised%20that%20a%20president%20could%20do%20a%20lot%20if%20he%20opted%20to%20follow%20his%20pledge%20in%20letter%20and%20spirit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIts%20operative%20part%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20will%20devote%20myself%20to%20the%20service%20and%20well-being%20of%20the%20people%20of%20India%E2%80%9D%20was%20interpreted%20by%20Narayanan%20as%20words%20that%20gave%20him%20the%20right%20to%20act%20like%20a%20%E2%80%98working%E2%80%99%20president.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheleaflet.in%2Fremembering-president-k-r-narayanan-defender-of-the-constitution%2F%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20him%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20post%20could%20be%20%E2%80%9Cused%20with%20a%20philosophy%20of%20indirect%20approach%E2%80%9D%20adding%20that%20there%20were%20%E2%80%9Cone%20or%20two%20things%E2%80%9D%20that%20could%20be%20done%20directly%20%E2%80%9Cin%20very%20critical%20times%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENarayanan%20was%20of%20the%20view%20that%20the%20president%20could%20exert%20%E2%80%9Cindirect%20influence%E2%80%9D%20on%20state%20affairs%20and%20that%20this%20was%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20most%20important%20role%20he%20can%20play.%E2%80%9D%20He%20believed%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthere%20must%20be%20some%20equation%20between%20the%20people%20and%20the%20President.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25190543%2FK-r-narayanan-1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22869%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%