ue%20faith%20and%20allegiance%E2%80%9D%20to%20the%20constitution.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENever%20too%20late%20is%20an%20idiomatic%20phrase%20that%20is%20almost%20a%20clich%C3%A9.%20One%20hopes%20that%20President%20Murmu%20is%20true%20to%20her%20responsibilities%20and%20uses%20the%20powers%20of%20her%20office.%20Nothing%20prevents%20her%20from%20visiting%20Manipur%20and%20commiserating%20with%20%E2%80%98her%20people%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPresident%20Murmu%20must%20recall%20the%20words%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20president%20that%20people%20look%20up%20to%20the%20president.%20Only%20she%20can%20decide%20what%20kind%20of%20president%20she%20wishes%20to%20be%20for%20the%20remaining%20years%20of%20her%20tenure.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3ENilanjan%20Mukhopadhyay%E2%80%99s%20latest%20book%20is%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Demolition%20and%20the%20Verdict%3A%20Ayodhya%20and%20the%20Project%20to%20Reconfigure%20India%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20His%20other%20books%20include%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20RSS%3A%20Icons%20of%20the%20Indian%20Right%20and%20Narendra%20Modi%3A%20The%20Man%2C%20The%20Times%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20He%20tweets%20at%20%40NilanjanUdwin.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690293643000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25191450%2FH20230621133757.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdroupadi-murmu-one-year-president-kalam-kr-narayanan%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20president%20is%20in%20fact%2C%20not%20just%20an%20all-abiding%20titular%20head%2C%20but%20has%20the%20capacity%20to%20act%20on%20her%20own.%20The%20decision%20to%20act%20or%20not%20is%20however%20the%20president%E2%80%99s.%20In%20this%20regard%2C%20President%20Murmu%20should%20follow%20the%20example%20of%20K.R.%20Narayanan%20and%20A.P.J.%20Abdul%20Kalam.%22%2C%22au