%20by%20the%20violence%20are%20people%20from%20my%20community%2C%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20tribes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20important%20to%20say%20this%20at%20the%20outset%20because%20when%20Modi%20spoke%2C%20he%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20number%20and%20identity%20of%20the%20perpetrators%20is%20one%20thing%20but%20the%20crime%20is%20an%20insult%20to%20the%20entire%20country.%E2%80%9D%20But%20the%20identity%20of%20the%20perpetrator(s)%20or%20the%20victim(s)%20is%20never%20a%20minor%20(or%20an%20irrelevant)%20detail%20in%20any%20conflict%2C%20where%20women%E2%80%99s%20bodies%20inevitably%20become%20a%20battleground%20for%20nationalism%20and%20identity%20assertion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnarendra-modi-manipur-response-humanity%5C%22%3EPM%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20Responses%20to%20Crises%20Show%20He%20Only%20Has%20Time%20for%20Politics%20%E2%80%93%20and%20Not%20Humanity%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20dominant%20Meiteis%20are%20seeking%20to%20restore%2C%20nay%20extend%20the%20limits%2C%20of%20their%20ancient%20Kangleipak%20kingdom%20into%20the%20hills.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20miniature%20Manipuri%20version%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-idea-of-akhand-bharat-smacks-of-imperial-aspirations%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Akhand%20Bharat%E2%80%99%20dream%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20built%20on%20imagined%20boundaries%2C%20a%20prayer.%20But%20it%20is%20a%20wish%20seemingly%20backed%20by%20the%20state%20government%2C%20led%20by%20chief%20minister%20Biren%20Singh%2C%20a%20Meitei%2C%20and%20a%20Meitei-dominated%20assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20civil%20war%20between%20armed%20Meitei%20and%20Kuki-Zo%20villagers%20and%20militants%2C%20Meitei%20women%20mobs%20now%20infamously%20known%20as%20%E2%80%98Meira%20Paibis%E2%80%99%20are%20using%20their%20bodies%20against%20the%20Army%20and%20Assam%20Rifles%20to%20allegedly%20protect%20their%20warring%20side%20and%20enable%20t