20were%20members%20of%20Meitei%20Leepun%20(whose%20founder%20openly%20expressed%20his%20loyalty%20to%20Singh%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DVDJnPewUhmU%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%253DVDJnPewUhmU%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1690355034036000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw3HYI3Sb1FM2_-CFxhNUg-M%5C%22%3Einterview%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20Karan%20Thapar)%2C%20Kangleipak%20Kunba%20Lup%2C%20Arambai%20Tenggol%2C%20and%20the%20World%20Meitei%20Council.%20They%20share%20much%20of%20their%20ideology%20with%20banned%20secessionist%20groups%20like%20United%20National%20Liberation%20Front%20(UNLF)%20and%20Kanglei%20Yawol%20Kunna%20Lup%20(KYKL)%2C%20who%20had%20killed%2019%20Indian%20Army%20personnel%20in%20a%202017%20ambush.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENone%20of%20these%20groups%20ever%20entered%20into%20formal%20negotiations%20with%20the%20Government%20of%20India%2C%20remaining%20true%20to%20their%20cause.%20With%20no%20desire%20to%20secede%20from%20India%2C%20these%20armed%20radical%20groups%20are%20a%20more%20acceptable%20version%20of%20the%20Meitei%20nationalistic%20cause%20for%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F21143828%2FF1airmNaMAEhHk3.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F21143828%2FF1airmNaMAEhHk3.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F21143828%2FF1airmNaMAEhHk3-300x135.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F21143828%2FF1airmNaMAEhHk3-1024x461.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-664373%5C%22%20hei