irst%20six%20months%20of%20this%20year%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20mission%20in%20Qatar%20experienced%20an%20exponential%2011%2C254%25%20rise%20in%20expenditure%20for%20legal%20assistance%20compared%20to%20last%20year%2C%20presumably%20linked%20to%20the%20ongoing%20case%20of%20eight%20former%20Indian%20naval%20officers%20who%20have%20been%20detained%20on%20unspecified%20charges%20for%20the%20past%2011%20months.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20sharp%20rise%20was%20revealed%20in%20a%20question%20addressed%20to%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20(MEA)%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20last%20Friday.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmea.gov.in%2Flok-sabha.htm%3Fdtl%2F36861%2FQUESTION_NO388_INDIAN_COMMUNITY_WELFARE_FUND%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20written%20answer%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20minister%20of%20state%20for%20external%20affairs%20V.%20Muraleedharan%20gave%20a%20detailed%20break-up%20of%20the%20funds%20utilised%20from%20the%20Indian%20Community%20Welfare%20Fund%20(ICWF)%20by%20each%20of%20the%20119%20Indian%20diplomatic%20missions%20and%20consulates%20around%20the%20world%20from%202019%20till%20June%202023.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20funding%20for%20the%20ICWF%20is%20generated%20through%20a%20charge%20on%20consular%20services%20offered%20by%20each%20mission.%20This%20fund%20is%20maintained%20in%20a%20separate%20account%20by%20the%20mission%2C%20and%20the%20authority%20to%20utilise%20the%20funds%2C%20within%20predetermined%20limits%2C%20is%20delegated%20to%20the%20head%20of%20the%20diplomatic%20outpost.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mea.gov.in%2Ficwf.htm%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20largely%20used%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20providing%20emergency%20medical%20care%2C%20air%20tickets%20for%20stranded%20Indians%2C%20legal%20assistance%2C%20boarding%20and%20lodging%20for%20distressed%20cases%2C%20transportation%20of%20mortal%20remains%20and%20payment%20of%20small%20fines%20for%20release%20from%20jails.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20MEA%E2%80%99s%20reply%2C%20dated%20July%2021%2C%20listed%20the%20expenditure%20details%20in%20two%20categories%20%E2%80%93%20legal%20assistance%20and%20transportation%20of%20mortal%20remains.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmea.gov.in%2FImages%2FCPV%2FLu388-21-07-2023-2-en.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20the%20details%20provided%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20expenditure%20of%20the%20Indian%20mission%20in%20Doha%20on%20financial%20assistance%20in%202019%20was%20Rs%201.87%20lakh.%20After%20a%20dip%20to%20just%20about%20Rs%2026%2C000%20in%20the%20pandemic%20year%20of%202020%2C%20it%20bounced%20back%20to%20Rs%201.79%20lakh%20the%20next%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThen%2C%20it%20increased%20sharply%20to%20Rs%207.4%20lakh%20within%20one%20year%20in%202022.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25181821%2FMEA-Data-III-1024x166.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25181821%2FMEA-Data-III-1024x166.png%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25181821%2FMEA-Data-III-300x49.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25181821%2FMEA-Data-III.png%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-665047%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22136%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESource%3A%20MEA%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20the%20current%20year%E2%80%99s%20expenditure%20puts%20that%20number%20to%20shade.%20The%20Indian%20embassy%20in%20Doha%2