n%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDogs%20might%20bite%20into%20the%20paper%20tableware%20and%20quickly%20swallow%20them.%20In%20such%20cases%2C%20edible%20plates%20cause%20no%20harm%20even%20if%20my%20dog%20consumes%20them%20as%20it%20is%20made%20of%20just%20rice%20straw%20and%20husk.%20These%20are%20not%20snack%20substitutes%2C%20but%20they%20can%20enjoy%20it%20when%20they%20are%20having%20food%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESneha%20also%20hosts%20dog-centric%20events%20like%20birthday%20parties%20and%20picnics%20where%20she%20has%20replaced%20plastic%20and%20paper%20cutlery%20with%20these%20alternatives.%20Rishabh%20says%20that%20the%20products%20are%20priced%20at%20Rs%20299%20for%20a%20pack%20of%2025%20animal%20edible%20plates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20this%20work%2C%20Rishabh%20and%20Rohan%20have%20been%20able%20to%20prevent%204%2C000%20kilos%20of%20agri-waste%20from%20being%20burned%20and%20saved%202%2C880%20kilos%20of%20single-use%20plastics%20from%20entering%20landfills%20and%20the%20sea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERishabh%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CEach%20work%20is%20special%20in%20its%20own%20way%2C%20but%20to%20be%20able%20to%20cater%20to%20the%20environment%20gives%20us%20far%20more%20satisfaction%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day.%20We%20are%20doing%20something%20that%20would%20have%20an%20impact%20on%20the%20environment%20while%20also%20earning%20money.%20It%20is%20a%20win-win.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20products%20are%20available%20for%20purchase%20on%20the%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fqudrat.co.in%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ewebsite%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20and%20are%20also%20available%20on%20Amazon%20and%20Flipkart.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Rishabh%20Suri%20and%20Sneha%20Sridhar.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22