ly%20call%20me%20%E2%80%98aunty%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds%20with%20a%20smile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Shashi%2C%20teaching%20these%20foreign%20tourists%20helps%20her%20feel%20empowered.%20%E2%80%9CI%20always%20believed%20in%20hard%20work.%20No%20one%20can%20defeat%20you%20if%20you%20believe%20in%20yourself.%20%3Cem%3ERoya%20daan%20nai%20milta%2C%20aur%20maangi%20bheek%20%3C%2Fem%3E(You%20won%E2%80%99t%20always%20get%20alms%20by%20crying).%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3EI%20have%20learnt%20that%20there%20is%20no%20point%20in%20crying%20in%20front%20of%20others%2C%20empower%20yourself%20to%20go%20on%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689946319000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fshashi-cooking-classes-3-1689859353.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D324582%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20losing%20her%20husband%2C%20Shashikala%20Sanadhya%20took%20care%20of%20her%20family%20by%20starting%20Shashi%20Cooking%20Classes.%20So%20far%2C%20she%20has%20taught%20over%201%2C000%20foreign%20tourists%20how%20to%20cook%20homely%20Indian%20food%20like%20chapati%2C%20naan%2C%20pakora%2C%20chutney%20and%20more.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A297%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F324582%2Fshashikala-sanadhya-gives-indian-food-cooking-lessons-for-foreign-tourists-in-udaipur%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Play%2C%20Learn%2C%20Grow%2C%20Repeat%3A%20A%20Peak%20Inside%20India%E2%80%99s%20Innovative%2C%20DIY%2C%20Sustainable%20Playgrounds%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20published%20in%20collaboration%20with%20EkStep%20Foundation.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Pooja%20Rai%20was%20a%20student%20of%20architecture%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F275217%2Fiit-kharagpur-innovation-oral-cancer-screening-cheap-device%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndian%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20(IIT)%2C%20Kharagpur%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20she%20would%20volunteer%20at%20Disha%20Seema%20Care%20Centre%2C%20a%20school%20for%20underprivileged%20children%20located%20on%20campus.%20During%20one%20visit%2C%20she%20observed%20a%20few%20girls%20playing%20on%20broken%20cement%20pipes%20while%20some%20construction%20work%20was%20going%20on%20nearby.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20extremely%20unsafe%20because%20you%20had%20wires%20coming%20out%20of%20the%20pipes%20and%20there%20were%20broken%20pieces%20of%20cement%20lying%20around.%20I%20also%20saw%20some%20boys%20at%20school%20trying%20to%20play%20a%20game%20of%20badminton%20with%20their%20slippers.%20Even%20though%20there%20was%20so%20much%20joy%20in%20that%20space%2C%20it%20just%20made%20me%20think%20that%20these%20children%20don%E2%80%99t%20even%20have%20access%20to%20something%20as%20simple%20as%20a%20playground.%20Talking%20to%20my%20friend%20that%20evening%2C%20we%20discussed%20how%20we%20could%20use%20all%20the%20design%20knowledge%20that%20we%20learned%20to%20build%20a%20playground%20for%20these%20kids%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rai%2C%20speaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20that%20Pooja%20and%20her%20batchmates%20were%20students%2C%20they%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20money.%20Instead%20of%20building%20a%20conventional%20playground%20with%20a%20jungle%20gym%2C%20merry%20go%20round%20and%20slides%2C%20they%20got%20innovative%2C%20brought%20a%20few%20tires%20together%2C%20and%20built%20a%20different%20kind%20of%20playground.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201193px)%20100vw%2C%201193px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com