ht%20thing%20to%20do.%20This%20way%20I%20would%20be%20able%20to%20reach%20the%20children%20living%20in%20the%20remotest%20areas%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20she%20moved%20to%20Komic%20and%20rented%20the%20place%20to%20start%20a%20free%20boarding%20school%20under%20her%20foundation%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0%20Planet%20Spiti%20Foundation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFollowing%20her%20father%E2%80%99s%20footsteps%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20think%20about%20it%2C%20my%20greatest%20motivation%20is%20my%20father.%20All%20of%20this%20work%20and%20my%20foundation%20are%20a%20tribute%20to%20him.%20I%E2%80%99m%20just%20continuing%20what%20he%20started%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoving%20to%20Komic%20was%20the%20first%20step%20towards%20her%20dream%20but%20what%20Portia%20was%20not%20aware%20of%20was%20the%20problems%20that%20would%20follow.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20major%20issue%20that%20I%20faced%20was%20convincing%20the%20parents%20to%20let%20their%20children%20go%20to%20school.%20They%20would%20say%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9Ckya%20karega%20padh%20ke%2C%20momo%20bech%20ke%20bhi%20paisa%20kama%20lega%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fem%3E(What%20will%20my%20child%20do%20with%20education%3F%20They%20can%20earn%20even%20by%20selling%20dumplings)%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20would%20spend%20hours%20talking%20to%20them%20and%20ask%20them%20to%20send%20them%20to%20school.%20At%20first%2C%20many%20were%20unmoved%20but%20slowly%20they%20caved%20in.%20Moreover%2C%20if%20I%20take%20a%20child%20and%20give%20them%20food%2C%20shelter%20and%20education%2C%20it%20lightens%20their%20burden.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fkomic-school-3-1689772598.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22