s%20weddings%20get%20larger%2C%20so%20is%20the%20wastage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20major%20waste%20producers%20in%20a%20wedding%20is%20food.%20According%20to%20an%20article%20in%20%3Cem%3EGround%20Report%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CAn%20average%20Indian%20wedding%20generates%20about%20200%E2%80%93300%20kg%20of%20food%20waste%20which%20amounts%20to%20almost%2020%25%20of%20the%20food%20going%20to%20waste.%20Cumulatively%2C%20it%20amounts%20to%20%2414%20billion%20worth%20of%20meals.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20decided%20on%20a%20menu%20that%20would%20involve%20less%20cutlery%20and%20chose%20dishes%20accordingly.%20We%20also%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20any%20plastic%20cups%20or%20water%20bottles.%20We%20rented%20steel%20cutlery%20from%20Adamya%20Chetana%2C%20a%20free%20cutlery%20bank.%20Food%20was%20served%20on%20banana%20leaves.%20We%20only%20used%20steel%20plates%20for%20the%20reception%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Anupama.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20would%20usually%20think%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F291582%2Fplan-green-eco-friendly-indian-wedding-with-ebikes-cycles-in-delhi%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elow-waste%20execution%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20only%20possible%20in%20small-scale%20weddings.%20But%20Anupama%20and%20Charulatha%20made%20sure%20the%20template%20worked%20for%20their%20big%20fat%20Indian%20wedding.%20They%20had%20more%20than%201%2C000%20guests%20for%20the%20reception%20and%20%3Cem%3Emuhurtam%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Yet%2C%20no%20plastic%20waste%20was%20generated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201125px)%20100vw%2C%201125px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-13-at-16.02.02-1689256290.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221125%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Flowers%20and%20lights%20were%20used%20for%20the%20wedding%20decoration.%5C%22%